er-bottom-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-image: url(http://www.wmzmd.com/statics/arrowleft-orange.gif); line-height: 21px; background-position: 0px 5px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">争议处理</h4>\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial; line-height: 21px;\">如果客户与网站之间发生任何争议，可依据当时双方所认定的协议或相关法律来解决。</span></div>', '', '', '', '0', '1', '1370409442', '', '0', 'http://116.255.154.183/article.php?id=84', '');
