/T 2874<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; color: red;\">【生产许可号】<span lang=\"EN-US\">XK16-108 3470<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; color: red;\">【生产日期】<span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; color: red;\">【商品产地】广东省中山</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class=\"apple-converted-space\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">&nbsp;</span></b></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; text-indent: 27.1pt; line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 255, 102);\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">古时候的人发现一种天然的草本植物，当它的叶子割开时，会分泌一种粘液，能很快使切口封闭和凝固。人们把这种粘液敷在割伤灼伤或者烂疮的伤口上，发现它具有神奇的疗效，伤口迅速止血排脓，并且日后几乎不留下任何疤痕。三千年来经过不断地运用研究和临床实验，这种神奇植物的粘液</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">-----</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">芦荟（</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">aloe-gel</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">）的医疗价值已被世界医学家肯定和认同。</span></b></span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 255, 102);\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; background-color: rgb(255, 102, 255);\"><br />\r\n</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 完美芦荟胶采用先进的冷冻稳定法，三十倍的浓缩从天然草本植物芦荟中萃取而成，其主要原料芦荟精华素来自美国，纯净度非常高，不含化学添加剂和杂质，无刺激性，包装精巧，携带方便。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\"><br />\r\n</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">护皮肤的功效！是美容精品；</span></b></span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 3.75pt 0cm; line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 255, 102);\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;【使用方法】</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; background-color: rgb(255, 102, 255);\"><br />\r\n</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 1</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">、如果有青春痘，那么洗脸后或你用器具清理里面的东西后将此凝胶抹在上面，早一次晚一次，一周后就有效果；</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\"><br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 2</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">、如果你的皮肤干性，那么一周两次用此做面膜，</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">(</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">用温热的水洗脸后抹一层厚一点的在脸上，半小时洗净再擦一层薄的</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">)</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">两周后，皱纹明显减少迹象，皮肤变白晰！这真的是好产品太好了；</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\"><br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 3</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">、完美芦荟胶还有杀菌功能，如果觉得阴道痕痒的话，也可以用完美芦荟胶擦一下，再配合完美沐浴露一起用很快就会不痒的了；</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\"><br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 4</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">、完美芦荟胶是一种高纯度的芦荟凝胶，必要时牙痛可含食；</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\"><br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 5</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">、每天出门前，涂在手和脸上，</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">(</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">要加点水，这样会更容易吸收</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">)</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">会有防晒作用，不会被阳光直接晒伤，有保护作用；</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\"><br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 6</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">、修复受伤的细胞如：意外伤</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">(</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">割伤、擦伤、烫伤</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">)</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">，若没有破口就用手的暗劲按摩使得皮肤发热，若用破口就先清洗后再涂上芦荟胶。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\"><br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 7</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">、完美芦荟胶还有防辐射功能，在您上网前用水稀释芦荟胶涂到脸部；</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\"><br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 8</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">、如果蚊虫叮咬后，可清洁皮肤后直接或用水稀释一下芦荟胶涂到感染处，有杀菌消炎的作用。</span></b></span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 255, 102);\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;【注意事项】置于阴凉干燥处，避免阳光直接照射。敏感肌肤者慎用。</span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><u><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">完美芦荟胶用途：</span></u></b><b><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0cm; background-color: yellow;\"><br />\r\n</span></u></b><u><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 黑体;\">冻伤</span></u><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">|</span></u><u><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 黑体;\">伤口<span lang=\"EN-US\">|</span>溃烂</span></u><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;|</span></u><u><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 黑体;\">脚气</span></u><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;|</span></u><u><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 黑体;\">鼻炎</span></u><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;|</span></u><u><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 黑体;\">黑斑</span></u><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">|</span></u><u><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 黑体;\">中耳炎</span></u><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">|</span></u><u><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 黑体;\">腮腺炎</span></u><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">|</span></u><u><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 黑体;\">青春痘</span></u><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;|</span></u><u><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 黑体;\">手术疤痕</span></u><b><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: 黑体;\">|</span></u></b><u><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 黑体;\">割伤<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;|</span>擦伤<span lang=\"EN-US\">│</span>口疮<span lang=\"EN-US\">│</span>美白<span lang=\"EN-US\">│</span>皮肤痕痒<span lang=\"EN-US\">│</span>皮肤开裂</span></u><b><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: 黑体;\">|</span></u></b><u><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 黑体;\">烫伤<span lang=\"EN-US\">│</span>痔疮<span lang=\"EN-US\">│</span>暗疮<span lang=\"EN-US\">│</span>蚊虫叮咬<span lang=\"EN-US\">│</span>保湿滋润<span lang=\"EN-US\">}</span>烧伤<span lang=\"EN-US\">│</span>湿疹<span lang=\"EN-US\">│</span>雀斑<span lang=\"EN-US\">│</span>唇边溃烂<span lang=\"EN-US\">│</span>消炎杀菌扭伤<span lang=\"EN-US\">│</span>冻疮<span lang=\"EN-US\">│</span>喉咙痛<span lang=\"EN-US\">│</span>防紫外线</span></u><b><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px;\">&nbsp;</span></u></b><b><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</span></u></b><b><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 18pt; line-height: 36px;\">&nbsp;</span></u></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 18pt; line-height: 36px;\"><br />\r\n<br />\r\n</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: 黑体; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><o:p></o:p></span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 27pt; line-height: 54px; font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">（一）芦荟胶美容</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 芦荟胶</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">有激活细胞活力，延缓皮肤衰老，收敛，调和皮肤，滋养皮肤，和保护皮肤的功</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">效。是美容佳品。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 1.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">激活细胞活力，延缓皮肤衰老</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;A.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">芦荟中的异柠</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">檬酸钙等成分能扩张毛细血管，促进微循环，增进皮肤细胞的物质代谢，强化细</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">胞活力。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">B.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">芦荟所含的超氧化物歧化酶，过氧化酶，维生素</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">C</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">，维生素</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">E</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">，胡萝卜素等自由基清除剂，能清除引起细胞衰老的自由基，延缓皮肤细胞衰老。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 2.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">收敛，调和皮肤芦荟天生的收敛作用，能使皮肤坚实而细致，预防皮肤松弛、起皱；粘蛋白成分能调节皮肤的水分和油脂，使皮肤保持在平衡状态。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 3.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">滋养皮肤</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">芦荟中含有的糖类，氨基酸，维生素</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">，矿物质，酵素，有机酸及水，是皮肤必需的营养素，芦荟中的这些成分分子小</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">，渗透力强，可进入皮肤的内层。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 4.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">保护皮肤</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;A.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">实验证明，芦荟液能在皮肤细胞表层形</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">成一层皮肤膜，能有效的锁住水分；</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">B.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">芦荟能吸收部分紫外线，有防晒作用；</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">C.&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">芦荟有杀菌，消炎，中和微生物毒素的作用，有效的预防各种微生物引起的皮肤</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">病。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 使用方法：洗脸后，将芦荟胶与水按</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">1</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">：</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">3</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">的比例</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">稀释后均匀的抹在脸上即可，每日</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">2-3</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">次，日间不宜抹太厚，睡前可抹厚些（作</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">营养面膜）。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<h2><b><span style=\"font-size: 27pt; line-height: 54px; font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">（二）黄褐斑，雀斑</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 27pt; line-height: 54px; font-family: inherit, serif; color: red;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 黄褐斑也称肝斑，是发生于</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">面部的一种色素沉着性皮肤病。妇女妊娠，月经失调，盆腔疾病，外在</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">表现为前额，颧，鼻，上唇等处片状黄褐色或咖啡色斑，大小不一，边缘清</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">楚，表面光滑，无自觉症状。有时黄褐斑互相融合，形成蝴蝶状外观。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 雀斑的发生可能和遗传及曝晒日光有关。大多在</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;6-7</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">岁开始出现，好发在面部，有时颈和手背等处也可发生，为针头至绿豆大小</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">黄褐或淡黑色斑点，成群或疏散分布，表面光滑，无自觉症状。夏季经强烈日晒</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">后，颜色加深，数目增多，冬季则颜色转淡，数目也减少。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 黄褐斑，雀斑有先天就易出现的人，但是经过紫</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">外线的辐射后，更易产生。化妆品过敏，精神紧张，偏食，肝脏，肾脏等内脏机</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">能低下等原因，使体内黑色素生成后沉着于体内，不能顺利排出，都可能是造成</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">的原因。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 防晒和脱色是祛斑的关键，</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">芦荟胶有利于祛斑，这是因为：</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 1.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">芦荟中含有芦荟素，蒽醌，肉桂酸酯等成分都</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">对部分紫外线有吸收作用，能隔绝部分日晒。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 2.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">芦荟胶中所含的氨基酸类，有机酸类，芦荟辛</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">等成分有抑制酪氨酸酶活性，阻碍黑色素形成的作用。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 3.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">芦荟能增强微循环，促进细胞的新陈代谢，逐渐去除皮肤中沉着的色素。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 治疗方法：洗脸后，将芦荟胶与水按</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">1</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">：</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">3</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">的比例</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">稀释后均匀的抹到脸上，在有斑的部位多做按摩，以促进皮肤吸收，增强微循环</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">1</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">日</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">3</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">次，日间的</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">2</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">次不宜抹得太厚，而睡前的涂抹可厚一些。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 说明：祛斑至少需要三个月才会显效，因为皮肤</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">中沉着的色素要通过细胞的新陈代谢才能脱掉，要耐心坚持治疗，另外也需查明</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">病因，去除病根才能治愈。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<h2><b><span style=\"font-size: 27pt; line-height: 54px; font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">（</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 27pt; line-height: 54px; font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">三）青春痘</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 27pt; line-height: 54px; font-family: inherit, serif; color: red;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 概述：青春痘是一种常见于青年人的毛曩，皮脂腺的慢性炎症。有以下别称：痤疮、寻常痤疮、暗疮、酒刺、青春蕾、发蕾、发疙瘩、粉刺等。好发于青年男女面部和胸、背部。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 病因：目前认为由内分泌旺</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">盛引起。体内的雄性激素（男女体内都有雄性激素）水平相对增高，使皮脂腺发</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">育旺盛，分泌增多；同时雄性激素又使毛曩，皮脂腺导管角化，栓塞，导致又多</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">又浓的皮脂不能完全排泄出去，逐渐积聚在毛曩口，加上毛曩壁上脱落的上皮细</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">胞，这样浓稠的皮脂就与脱落的细胞混合在一起，成为干酪样物质栓塞在毛曩口</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">内，就形成了痤疮（白头粉刺）。疮疱顶端部分逐渐干燥，又经过空气的氧化作</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">用及尘土的污染而变色，便形成常见的黑头粉刺，由于粉刺的挤压和局部游离脂</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">肪酸的侵入，引起毛曩，皮脂腺的炎症反应，出现丘疹，脓疱，结节，脓肿及瘢</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">痕等各种表现。</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 方法：成熟的有脓包的豆豆，你可以用洗干净的手把脓包挤掉，然后再伤口上擦上芦荟胶，可以多用一点点。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><o:p></o:p></span></b>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><b><span style=\"font-size: 24pt; line-height: 48px; font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">（四）芦荟胶的美容用法</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 1</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">芦荟胶可以用来当面霜</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 当面霜的话用量不能太多，多按膜让皮肤充分吸</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">收．如果用量太多，皮肤吸收不完，容易造成搓泥现象．因为芦荟多的时候可能有点粘的感觉．冬天擦了芦荟胶后保湿力度可能不够，会觉得不油腻，非常的清爽，用了非常舒服．</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 2</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">芦荟胶可以用来做面膜</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 有两种用法：</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 一种是洁面后直接涂上厚厚的芦荟胶，第二天洗掉，感觉皮肤非常的光滑．而且如果你脸上有发红发痒的症状，用它做面膜后这些症状会改善很多。</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 另外一种用法是洁面后先涂上厚厚的芦荟胶打底</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">，然后敷上泡了芦荟藓汁或者是纯露或者是其他没有刺激性的水水的纸膜，大约</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">２０分钟后拿掉，皮肤会感觉吸足了水分，水水的，嫩嫩的，而且芦荟胶有非常</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">好的修复作用，能很好的修复皮肤破损组织。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 3</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">芦荟胶可以用来调橄榄油</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 弄一点芦荟胶在手心，然后滴一滴橄榄油，混匀</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">，用来擦脸或者当眼霜，滋润抗皱的效果很不错。这种用法橄榄油不要用太多。</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">一滴就足够了，用多了皮肤吸收不完会很油腻。</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 4</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">芦荟胶与隔离霜混合</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 芦荟胶可以和隔离霜混合后使用，这样不会搓泥</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">，而且很滋润，不会觉得隔离霜太厚太干，而且芦荟胶本身也具有一定的隔离作</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">用，两者混合隔离效果会更好。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 5</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">芦荟胶缓解疼痛、发痒、发红</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 如果被蚊虫叮咬了或者皮肤弄破了、烫伤了什么</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">的，都可以用上芦荟胶，它独特的修复、消炎抑菌作用，能够缓解疼痛、发痒、</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">发红等症状，能促进伤口的愈合。</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 6</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">芦荟胶做导入</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 方法很简单的，就是擦上任何一款你要导入的精</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">华后，再把芦荟胶厚厚的涂在脸上做导入，芦荟就是起滑的作用，就像在医院做</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">超音波检查时擦的藕和剂</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">。</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px; font-family: inherit, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"line-height: 18px; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp;<b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 7</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">芦荟胶</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit, serif;\">+</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">晚霜</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"line-height: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: 宋体;\">在晚霜里加一点点芦荟胶，这样涂在脸上吸收起</span><b style=\"line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 宋体;\">来很快，</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: 宋体;\">而且还感觉水水的。芦荟胶的修复作用加</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: 宋体;\">上晚霜足够的补水保湿作用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt;\">,</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: 宋体;\">两全其美。</span></b></p>\r\n<div class=\"marginleft\" style=\"margin-left: 14px; font-family: Simsun;\">\r\n<div id=\"txt_ulli\" style=\"width: 706px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span id=\"Label_Content\"> </span></div>\r\n</div>', 'images/201306/thumb_img/186_thumb_G_1370106671707.gif', 'images/201306/goods_img/186_G_1370106671404.jpg', 'images/201306/source_img/186_G_1370106671959.gif', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1369456004', '2', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1371240393', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '');
