p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:黑体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">产品价格：￥<span lang=\"EN-US\">129<o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><img src=\"http://www.perfect99.com/product_pic/BigImages/qtz.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">芦荟多用途清洁剂 净含量：<span lang=\"EN-US\">1L<o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">产品说明：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">浓缩环保温和配方，采用最新的三元复合增效技术，复配多种温和表面活性剂，泡沫丰富，易于清洗，不留残渍，全方位清除污垢；更添加肌氨酸衍生物、库拉索芦荟叶汁粉等有效清除污垢的同时，温和呵护您的双手。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">主要成分：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">水、<span lang=\"EN-US\">C14-16 </span>烯烃磺酸钠、月桂醇硫酸酯铵、<span lang=\"EN-US\">C12-14 </span>仲链烷醇聚醚<span lang=\"EN-US\">-9</span>、月桂醇聚醚硫酸酯钠、椰油酰胺丙基胺氧化物、氯化钠、月桂酰肌氨酸钠、聚乙二醇<span lang=\"EN-US\">-12</span>、库拉索芦荟（<span lang=\"EN-US\">ALOE BARBADENSIS</span>）叶汁粉、<span lang=\"EN-US\">EDTA </span>二钠、甲基异噻唑啉酮、甲基氯异噻唑啉酮、柠檬酸、香精、<span lang=\"EN-US\">CI 19140</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">CI 42090</span>。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">适用范围及使用方法：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、清洁地板、墙壁、浴缸、瓷砖、塑料制品等家居用品：每<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>升水加<span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span>毫升（<span lang=\"EN-US\">2/3</span>瓶盖）清洁剂，洗涤后用清水洗净。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、清洗玻璃、木制家具等家居用品：每<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>升水加<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>毫升（<span lang=\"EN-US\">1/3</span>瓶盖）清洁剂，洗涤后用清水洗净。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、洗车：用<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>升水加<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>毫升（<span lang=\"EN-US\">1/3</span>瓶盖）清洁剂，洗涤后用清水洗净。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、洗手：用稀释清洁剂清洗，然后用清水冲净。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">（可根据洗涤需要，适当调整稀释浓度。）<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">芦荟餐具洗洁精 净含量：<span lang=\"EN-US\">1L<o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">产品说明：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">浓缩型清洁配方，采用<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>绿色表面活性剂<span lang=\"EN-US\">&mdash;&mdash;</span>烷基葡糖苷<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>配合多种清洁成分，安全组合，高效去除餐具污垢，易于漂净，无毒无残留，更添加库拉索芦荟叶汁粉，有效呵护您的双手。适合于各类餐具、茶具的洗涤。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">主要成分：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">水、<span lang=\"EN-US\">C14-16</span>烯烃磺酸钠、<span lang=\"EN-US\">C12-14</span>仲链烷醇聚醚<span lang=\"EN-US\">-9</span>、月桂醇聚醚硫酸酯钠、月桂醇硫酸酯铵、癸基葡糖苷、椰油酰胺丙基胺氧化物、氯化钠、库拉索芦荟（<span lang=\"EN-US\">ALOE BARBADENSIS</span>）叶汁粉、羟苯甲酯、香精。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">产品特点：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、独特的<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>多元洗涤系统（<span lang=\"EN-US\">MDS</span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>，融合多种特殊的表面活性剂，可迅速溶解、去除各类餐具及茶具的顽固油垢和食物污垢；<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、泡沫丰富<span lang=\"EN-US\">&mdash;</span>易于冲洗，去污迅速<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>不留残渍；<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、浓缩配方<span lang=\"EN-US\">&mdash;</span>稀释使用，经济实惠，效果更佳；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、性质温和<span lang=\"EN-US\">&mdash;</span>含芦荟提取物及椰子油衍生物，中性配方，不损伤幼嫩肌肤；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、天然品质<span lang=\"EN-US\">&mdash;</span>内含氨基酸类表面活性剂，高效去污，安全环保；<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、功效独特<span lang=\"EN-US\">&mdash;</span>采用特效抗菌剂，可去除污染物，有益健康；<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、香味独特，清新怡人。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">适用范围及使用方法：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、可用于清洗陶瓷、塑料、玻璃、金属等各类餐具和茶具。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、每<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>升水加<span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span>～<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>毫升（<span lang=\"EN-US\">1/3</span>瓶盖、视水量及不洁净程度而定）洗洁精进行洗涤、浸泡<span lang=\"EN-US\"> ,</span>然后用清水洗净。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">芦荟蔬果洁净剂 净含量：<span lang=\"EN-US\">300ml<o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">产品说明<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">浓缩型清洁配方，采用<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>绿色表面活性剂<span lang=\"EN-US\"> &mdash;&mdash;</span>烷基葡糖苷<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>配合水果来源的酶制剂等多种清洁成分，高效组合，快速乳化、去除蔬菜和水果表面污垢及残留农药，易于漂净，无毒无残留，更添加库拉索芦荟叶汁粉，有效呵护您的双手。本品不含香精、色素。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">适合于各类蔬菜、瓜果的洗涤。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">主要成分：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">水、<span lang=\"EN-US\">C14-16</span>烯烃磺酸钠、<span lang=\"EN-US\">C12-14</span>仲链烷醇聚醚<span lang=\"EN-US\">-9</span>、月桂醇聚醚硫酸酯钠、月桂醇硫酸酯<span lang=\"EN-US\">TEA</span>盐、癸基葡糖苷、椰油酰胺丙基胺氧化物、库拉索芦荟（<span lang=\"EN-US\">ALOE BARBADENSIS</span>）叶汁粉、木瓜蛋白酶、羟苯甲酯。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">使用方法：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">每升水加<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>～<span lang=\"EN-US\">2ml</span>（视水量及不洁净程度而定）洁净剂浸泡<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>～<span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span>分钟，进行洗涤，然后用清水洗净。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">注意事项：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">如不慎入眼，请即用清水洗净。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"marginleft\" style=\"margin-left: 14px;\">\r\n<div id=\"txt_ulli\" style=\"width: 706px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span id=\"Label_Content\"> </span></div>\r\n</div>', 'images/201306/thumb_img/187_thumb_G_1370058791687.gif', 'images/201306/goods_img/187_G_1370058791338.jpg', 'images/201306/source_img/187_G_1370058791749.gif', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1369456004', '95', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1371008228', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '');
