>10</span>克<span lang=\"EN-US\">&times;30</span>包<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:黑体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">产品价格：￥<span lang=\"EN-US\">170<o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><img src=\"http://www.perfect99.com/product_pic/BigImages/new_GAOXIANLE.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:24.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">肠<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>通无阻 其乐融融<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n24.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\ncolor:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:26.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;\r\nmso-themetint:153;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">----</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:26.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#FABF8F;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">完美高纤乐</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">完美高纤乐的主要成份是西莲壳、沙棘粉和草莓粉。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">西莲壳</span></b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">是迄今人类发现的食物中膳食纤维含量最高的物质，因此被誉为<b><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>纤维巨人<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span></b>。每单位的西莲壳含有<span lang=\"EN-US\">86%</span>的膳食纤维，且其中的<b>可溶性纤维相当于我们熟悉的燕麦的<span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span>倍</b>。西莲壳能促进肠道蠕动、清洁肠道、增加肠道内有益菌群数量。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">沙棘果</span></b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">被蒙古族、藏族人民尊为<b><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>高原圣果<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span></b>，已有上千年历史。 沙棘果含有丰富的维生素、矿物质和不饱和脂肪酸。其中维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">E</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">&beta;&mdash;</span>胡萝卜素、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">K</span>的含量几乎居一切果蔬之冠。尤以维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>含量最高，每百克含量高达<span lang=\"EN-US\">800--850 </span>毫克，比猕猴桃高<span lang=\"EN-US\">3--4</span>倍。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">草莓</span></b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">富含氨基酸、果糖、果胶、多种维生素和矿物质。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">一包<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>克高纤乐中含有的膳食纤维相当于<span lang=\"EN-US\">1000</span>克葡萄、<span lang=\"EN-US\">500</span>克蕃茄或<span lang=\"EN-US\">300</span>克苹果的含量。因此完美高纤乐较之完美高纤餐，有以下三个特点：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:72.8pt;text-indent:-45.75pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#FABF8F;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1、<span style=\"font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">保健功能更全面<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span></span></b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#FABF8F;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">在调节肠胃功能、排除宿便、避免便秘、预防肠道疾病、降血脂和预防心血管病、降血糖及预防糖尿病、控制肥胖、美容等基础上增加了免疫调节、抗肿瘤、抗炎生肌、促进组织再生，健脑益智，促进儿童生长发育和抗衰老的作用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:72.8pt;text-indent:-45.75pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#FABF8F;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2、<span style=\"font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">口味更佳<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span></span></b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#FABF8F;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">高纤乐是草莓口味，<b>酸甜爽口</b>，入口清新，喝起来很舒服。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:72.8pt;text-indent:-45.75pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#FABF8F;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">3、<span style=\"font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">无饱足感<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span></span></b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#FABF8F;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">喝后不感饱胀，不影响吃其它食物。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">服用方法：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">将完美高纤乐粉剂倒入杯中，用温开水冲调，<b>搅拌均匀后马上食用</b>，食后多喝水。第一个月可每日早晚各服用一包，以后每天一次。如非用作减肥，可在饭后或空腹服用；作减肥用，可在每日用餐前<span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span>分钟饮用半包至一包。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">注意事项：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">服用完美高纤乐后要多喝水，完美高纤乐<b>不能用沸水冲调</b>，小部分人服用的前几天可能有腹痛的好转反应，但不久后会自然消失。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">完美高纤乐针对现代人摄入膳食纤维严重不足的现状，采用消除人体垃圾，补充人体必须的营养素<span lang=\"EN-US\">--<b>&ldquo;</b></span><b>既清又补，以清为主<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span></b>的保健方法，对排除人体内的毒源<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span><b>宿便</b>，调节胃肠功能，预防肠道疾病具有独到的功效！<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">说明：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">完美高纤乐富含膳食纤维，膳食纤维的摄入也不是越多越好，摄入过多膳食纤维会干扰人体对其它营养物质的吸收，特别是<b>老人、小孩和孕妇要避免摄入过多</b>。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:44.05pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:22.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">产 品 问 答</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">问：完美高纤乐的<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>高纤<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>是什么<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">答：<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>高纤乐<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>的成份中含有一种称作<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>纤维巨人<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>的西莲壳。因为到目前为止，<b>全世界还没有发现比西莲壳的膳食纤维含量更高的物质。</b>我们拿日常生活中的事物来举例说明。一包<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>高纤乐<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>中含有的膳食纤维相当于二斤的葡萄、一斤的大米、一斤番茄、或是六两的苹果各自的膳食纤维含量。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">问：完美高纤乐的膳食纤维是什么<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">答：<b>膳食纤维主要来自水果、蔬菜、豆类和谷类。</b>有医学报道表示现在先进国家中，每四个人当中就有一个人遭受不同程度的肠道消化毛病。其最大原因就是因为摄人太少的膳食纤维。膳食纤维可分为<b>可溶性纤维和不溶性纤维</b>两种。可溶性纤维能部分被肠道菌群分解和发酵，产生有机酸，增加肠道酸度，有利于有益菌群的生长，刺激肠粘膜蠕动。此外，未被消化的膳食纤维形成的食物残渣能改变粪便形状，刺激结肠运动，促进排便。不溶性纤维具有较强的持水性，吸水膨胀后可形成软绵海绵体，可阻碍小肠对毒素的吸收，可包裹代谢物，清洁肠道，正常地将有毒物质排出体外，从而逐渐消除便秘现象。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">3、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">问：食用纤维能<span lang=\"EN-US\">**</span>便秘吗<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">答：<b>食用膳食纤维是<span lang=\"EN-US\">**</span>便秘的根本调节法。</b>目前，国际上鼓励人们通过调节饮食习惯，让人们在自身不伤害身体的情况下彻底消除便秘。食物调节主要是食用膳食纤维，它在我们体内担当一个很重要的作用，膳食纤维在小肠内不会被吸收，但在结肠中可以部分破裂分解吸收肠道中水份残渣并蓬松变软，使废物更滑脱、迅速、容易排除体外。这不但不会伤害身体，反而迅速补充人体所需要的其他营养素，使之更好的促进您的健康。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">4、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">问：为什么此产品叫<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>乐<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>而不叫餐<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">答：所谓<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>乐<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>就是<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>乐趣<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>，以前我们吃高纤餐，有人反应味道不太棒和吃了就很饱，他们的矛盾是<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>高纤餐<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rsquo;&rsquo;</span>很好很想多吃，但又不能只吃它不吃其它食物。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">现在我们有了<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>高纤乐<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>，它是一种天然、安全、营养丰富的物质。天然的草莓口味，适合老人、小孩、女士、男士等各类型人士食用。如果您愿意，可以当它是一种饮料，随冲随饮，酸甜爽滑、入口清新，喝起来很舒服，所以我们叫它<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>高纤乐<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">5、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">问：完美高纤乐的主要成份有什么功效<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">答：<span lang=\"EN-US\">①</span>西莲壳<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span>西莲壳含有<span lang=\"EN-US\">86%</span>的膳食纤维，包括可溶性纤维和不溶性纤维。西莲壳（膳食纤维）即象一把柔软的刷子，可清除粘藏在大肠皱壁上的废物，就像人体肠道中的清洁工，不断帮你清洁肠道。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">②</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">沙棘粉<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span>沙棘粉中富含维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">E</span>、甘露醇、黄酮醇、多种氨基酸、微量元素等。维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>对人体的新陈代谢有着重要的促进作用，对<b>坏血病、贫血、感冒、外伤</b>等具有显著的疗效。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">③</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">草莓<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span>中国的医学史中就有记载：草莓具有<b>清热气、解暑、止渴、利尿、润喉</b>等功效。我们选用纯天然草莓粉和草莓果肉，因它含有丰富维生素、钙、磷等多种矿物质，对生长发育有很大的帮助。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">6、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">问：<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>高纤乐<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>适合什么人群食用？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">答：由于草莓味道好还有很多优点，<b>适合各类人群食用</b>，相信您一家大小，不论是老人、小孩或孕妇，有便秘又不愿意吃其他药物或食物时，一杯<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>高纤乐<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>不但能给您解决疾苦，还会带给他更多的乐趣。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">7、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">问：高纤乐、营养餐中的阿斯巴甜和果糖有何区别？糖尿病人可否服用高纤乐、营养餐？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">答：<b>果糖是一种单糖</b>。我们的营养餐和高纤乐中所含的<b>阿斯巴甜是一种低热量甜味剂</b>，食用后便会分解为蛋白质成分，可被人体吸收，消化及正常代谢。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">8、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">问：阿斯巴甜在完美氨基酸片、高纤乐、营养餐中所起的作用？阿斯巴甜听说在外国已禁用，是否刺激大脑神经？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">答：<b>阿斯巴甜是一种安全可靠的低热量甜味剂</b>，自<span lang=\"EN-US\">1981</span>年美国食品和药物管理局（<span lang=\"EN-US\">FDA</span>）标准通过后，目前已被超过<span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span>多个国家及多个国际权威组织认可，其中包括世界卫生组织（<span lang=\"EN-US\">WHO</span>）、<span lang=\"EN-US\">JECFA</span>、美国、加拿大糖尿病协会等。中国于<span lang=\"EN-US\">1986</span>年正式批准阿斯巴甜在食品中使用，可适用于各种食品及保健食品，至于刺激大脑神经，那是根本没有的事，且无科学证据，否则，为何<span lang=\"EN-US\">FDA</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">WHO</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">JEC-FA</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">USA</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">CNS</span>能认可。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">9、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">问：高纤乐很红，是否有色素<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">答：高纤乐带点粉红是草莓粉天然颜色，且我们产品不添加任何色素。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"marginleft\" style=\"margin-left: 14px; font-family: Simsun;\">\r\n<div id=\"txt_ulli\" style=\"width: 706px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span id=\"Label_Content\"> </span></div>\r\n</div>', 'images/201305/thumb_img/193_thumb_G_1369843705524.png', 'images/201305/goods_img/193_G_1369843705517.jpg', 'images/201305/source_img/193_G_1369843705483.png', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1369456004', '89', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1371231021', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '');
INSERT INTO `ecs_goods` ( `goods_id`, `cat_id`, `goods_sn`, `goods_name`, `goods_name_style`, `click_count`, `brand_id`, `provider_name`, `goods_number`, `goods_weight`, `market_price`, `shop_price`, `promote_price`, `promote_start_date`, `promote_end_date`, `warn_number`, `keywords`, `goods_brief`, `goods_desc`, `goods_thumb`, `goods_img`, `original_img`, `is_real`, `extension_code`, `is_on_sale`, `is_alone_sale`, `is_shipping`, `integral`, `add_time`, `sort_order`, `is_delete`, `is_best`, `is_new`, `is_hot`, `is_promote`, `bonus_type_id`, `last_update`, `goods_type`, `seller_note`, `give_integral`, `rank_integral`, `suppliers_id`, `is_check` ) VALUES  ('194', '28', 'FM30', '完美高纤餐（盒）', '+', '21', '12', '', '9999', '15.000', '135.00', '135.00', '0.00', '0', '0', '200', '', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:24.0pt;font-family:黑体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">完美高纤餐（盒）产品说明<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:黑体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:黑体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">产品代号：<span lang=\"EN-US\">FM30<o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:黑体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">产品规格：<span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span>克<span lang=\"EN-US\">&times;30</span>包<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:黑体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">产品价格：￥<span lang=\"EN-US\">135<o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><img src=\"http://www.perfect99.com/product_pic/BigImages/new-GAOXIANCAN.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">完美高纤餐的主要成份是西莲壳、燕麦、麦芽精、糙米粉、大豆、玉粟黍等。其中西莲壳和燕麦中膳食纤维含量很高。西莲壳是迄今人类发现的食物中膳食纤维含量最高的物质，因此被誉为<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>纤维巨人<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>。每单位的西莲壳含有<span lang=\"EN-US\">86%</span>的膳食纤维。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">膳食纤维是指食物中不能被人体消化吸收的多糖类和木质素。膳食纤维按其在水中的溶解性能，大致可分为不溶性膳食纤维和可溶性膳食纤维两大类。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">膳食纤维有以下理化特征<span lang=\"EN-US\">:<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 72pt; text-indent: -45pt; line-height: 150%;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">1、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">较强的持水性 膳食纤维的化学结构中含有许多亲水基因，因此持水性强。膳食纤维的持水性可以增加人体排便的体积和速度，减轻直肠内的压力，同时也减轻了泌尿系统的压力，从而可缓解膀胱炎、膀胱结石和肾结石的症状，并能使毒素迅速排出体外。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;text-indent:-45.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">2、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">清扫肠道的作用<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>膳食纤维在结肠中可部分破裂分解，像海绵一样吸收肠道中的水分和残渣并膨松变软，能像柔软的刷子一样清除粘藏在大肠皱壁内的宿便，使寄生的有害菌大大减少，并在大肠内壁形成一层光滑的薄膜，使宿便更容易从肠壁剥离、滑脱而排出体外。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;text-indent:-45.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">3、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">对有机化合物的吸附作用<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>膳食纤维表面的活性因子可吸附胆固醇和胆汁酸等有机化合物，抑制人体对它们的吸收。此外膳食纤维还能吸附肠道内的有害物质、化学药品和有毒药品，并能促使它们排出体外。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;text-indent:-45.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">4、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">类似填充剂的作用膳食纤维吸水膨胀时会在胃肠道占据一定体积，引起饱腹感。同时，膳食纤维的存在也影响机体对其它成分的消化吸收，因而对肥胖有较好的预防效果。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;text-indent:-45.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">5、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">改变肠道系统中的微生物群系组成 可溶性纤维能部分被肠道菌群分解和发酵，肠道内膳食纤维含量高时，会诱导出大量好气菌群来代替原来的厌气菌群，这些好气菌很少产生致癌物。同时，纤维在肠道中代谢产生大量短链羟酸，如乙酸、乳酸等。这对形成肠道良好的环境有重要的生理作用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">富含膳食纤维的完美高纤餐具有以下保健功效：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:64.35pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">1、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">控制肥胖<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">由于膳食纤维能增强胃部的饱足感，如果在饭前服用高纤餐，就可以减少人的饭量，而高纤餐含的热能比一般食物中的热能低很多，这就会使人体每天摄入的总热能降低。并且服用高纤餐后还会影响人体对其它高热能食物的消化吸收，减少对其的热能利用。这样就能帮助人们减少热能的摄入。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">如果在服用高纤餐的同时，增加适量的有氧运动，使身体热能消耗量大于摄入量，就能起到很好的减肥作用。与节食减肥不同，服用高纤餐减肥不需要忍受饥饿的痛苦，也不会因为减肥节食，身体缺乏维生素和矿物质而影响健康。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:64.35pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">2、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">调节胃肠功能、排除宿便，避免便秘，预防肠道疾病<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">膳食纤维有较强的持水性，增加了粪便容积，能促进肠道蠕动，有利通便；能清扫肠道，排除宿便，防止便秘；改善肠道内细菌群，抑制有害物质的吸收并促进排泄，具有解毒、缓解疾病和预防结肠癌的作用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:64.35pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">3、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">美容<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">宿便、便秘是青春痘的直接病因。皮肤是内脏的镜子，肠道不健康会引起肤色灰暗、无光泽、皮肤粗糙、多皱纹。宿便、便秘产生的毒素也会引起皮肤细胞老化。高纤餐能排除宿便、解除便秘，所以有美容的功效。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:64.35pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">4、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">降血脂和预防心血管病<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">膳食纤维具有降低血脂和血清胆固醇的作用。膳食纤维能吸收胆汁酸和胆固醇，减少肠壁对胆固醇的吸收，并促进胆汁酸从粪便中排出，加快胆固醇的代谢，从而使体内胆固醇的含量下降。麦芽麸皮水溶性纤维对降低胆固醇和预防心血管疾病效果特别明显。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:64.35pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">5、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">降血糖及预防糖尿病<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">膳食纤维可改善末梢组织对胰岛素的感受，降低对胰岛素的需求，从而可调节糖尿病患者的血糖水平。另外，由于高纤餐中的麦芽精、糙米粉、大豆、玉粟黍成分中含有高品质的蛋白质（蛋白质互补作用）、维生素和矿物质。服用高纤餐也能给人体补充营养素，增强体质。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">服用方法：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">将完美高纤餐粉剂倒入杯中，用温开水冲调，搅拌均匀后马上食用，食后多喝水。第一个月可每日早晚各服用一包，以后每天一次。如非用作减肥，可在饭后或空腹服用；作减肥用，可在每日用餐前<span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span>分钟饮用半包至一包。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">注意事项：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">服用完美高纤餐或高纤乐后要多喝水，完美高纤餐和高纤乐不能用沸水冲调，小部分人服用的前几天可能有腹痛的好转反应，但不久后会自然消失。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">完美高纤餐针对现代人摄入膳食纤维严重不足的现状，采用消除人体垃圾，补充人体必须的营养素<span lang=\"EN-US\">&mdash;&ldquo;</span>既清又补，以清为主<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>的保健方法，对排除人体内的毒源<span lang=\"EN-US\">&mdash;</span>宿便，调节胃肠功能，预防肠道疾病具有独到的功效！<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">说明：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">完美高纤餐富含膳食纤维，膳食纤维的摄入也不是越多越好，摄入过多膳食纤维会干扰人体对其它营养物质的吸收，特别是老人、小孩和孕妇要避免摄入过多。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:22.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">产品问答<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">、问：有顾客反映高纤餐用<span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span>度的水冲出来浓度很稀，过了七八分钟后还是一样，请问为什么<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：高纤餐的原料是纯天然植物，每批会有少许差别，但都会在合格范围内，我们才会用于生产。该顾客所见现象是在合格范围内的。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">、问：高纤餐里的黑粒是什么<span lang=\"EN-US\">?</span>为何有些高纤餐用热水冲过后好久都不变稠<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：黑颗粒是原料中的一种植物种皮。至于不变稠，是食物溶水分解快慢现象，出厂的高纤餐质量稳定，均在合格范围内、不用怕。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">、问：高纤餐、完美营养餐、矿物晶同期食用，时间差有何要求<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：如同期食用，建议完美营养餐在早晨食用，高纤餐在晚上，而矿物晶不分时段，按自己喜好随时饮用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">、问：吃完美高纤餐是否能够减肥<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：完美高纤餐内含有大显的膳食纤维<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span>车前子壳，可促进肠胃蠕动，缩短食物在消化道内的时间，而且高纤餐在进入肠胃后、因吸收水份而膨胀，有饱胀的感觉、可减少食欲。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">、问：为什么高纤餐对动脉硬化及冠心病人有帮助<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：高纤餐中所含大量水溶性纤维可帮助降低胆固醇、降血脂，同时，高纤餐中特别添加的燕麦含有丰富的亚油酸，能调整胆固醇正常的代谢过程，软化血管，预防动脉硬化及冠心病的发生。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">、问：为什么高纤餐强调用<span lang=\"EN-US\">70</span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n宋体;color:#00B050\">℃</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">温开水冲食，而且要即冲即饮<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：因为高纤餐主要成份是车前子壳，该物质遇热水会膨胀凝结，会变得很稠不好喝，因此，不能用太热的开水冲泡，而且冲泡后要马上喝完。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:#00B050\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050\">、问：为什么高纤餐可以起到美容作用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\">?<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：高纤餐是国家卫生部批准的保健食品，具润肠通便之效，能帮助我们清洁肠道，简单地说，就是清洗肠道内肮脏的东西，所以令人健康、容光焕发。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">8</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">、问：对初次食用高纤餐的朋友有何好建议<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>答：每天早晚食用一包，至少维持一个月，然后每天一包，三个月后自然见效。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:22.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"marginleft\" style=\"margin-left: 14px; font-family: Simsun;\">\r\n<div id=\"txt_ulli\" style=\"width: 706px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span id=\"Label_Content\"> </span></div>\r\n</div>', 'images/201305/thumb_img/194_thumb_G_1369843453564.png', 'images/201305/goods_img/194_G_1369843453111.jpg', 'images/201305/source_img/194_G_1369843453119.png', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1369456004', '88', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1371182768', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '');
