\">132</span>克<span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span>瓶<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:黑体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">产品价格：￥<span lang=\"EN-US\">208</span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"http://www.perfect99.com/product_pic/BigImages/new_kuangwujing-%20ping.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">主要成份：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">一、<strong>芦荟提取物</strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>选用由国际芦荟协会提供的纯种美国库拉索芦荟，经冷冻稳定法淬取而成。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">二、<strong>花粉、蜂皇浆</strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>采用的花粉已先行经过低温冷冻破壁粉碎法处理，使人体吸收率接近<span lang=\"EN-US\">100%</span>，而一般未经破壁处理的花粉吸收率仅为<span lang=\"EN-US\">20-30%</span>。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">三、<strong>多种矿物质</strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>是从美国内华达州的深海河床淬取提炼而来，经过分离和再融合，使每一种矿物质的份量都符合人体需求的和谐比例，并使其保持易被人体高效吸收的化学状态。维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>经过稳定处理，使其不易氧化分解。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">完美芦荟矿物晶中各种成份数量比例系经过长期大量的科学研究及临床实验后多次调整，最终确定的。使得各成份功效相辅相成，相得益彰。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">完美芦荟矿物晶具有符合最权威的预防保健学说<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>分子矫正学说<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>所提出的<strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span></strong><strong>健康三要件<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span></strong>的三大显著保健功效：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">㈠、<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></i><!--[endif]--><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">清理排毒</span></em><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">完美芦荟矿物晶能够帮助人体清理排除累积在大肠皱壁、血液中和体内的废物和毒素，这是因为：芦荟能促进血液循环，加速新陈代谢，并能增强人体自身的排毒机能（如免疫力），使人体清除排泄废物和毒素的能力增强；芦荟具有清血作用，能有效清除血液和血管中的异物。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">⑶</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">芦荟具有解毒的作用，其所含有的<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>氨基乙酸<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>等物质能够与许多有毒的分泌物相结合，而将它转换成无害的形式；芦荟可使积存在体内的病毒、化学毒素等产生自坏作用后被排出。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">㈡、加强新陈代谢，调理人体各大系统</span></em><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">完美芦荟矿物晶能够加强人体正常的新陈代谢，这是因为：芦荟矿物晶含有人体所需的全面、均衡的营养素，能被人体有效地消化吸收，能够满足人体新陈代谢的物质需要；芦荟矿物晶清理排除人体内妨碍新陈代谢物质交接的废物和毒害人体细胞组织的毒素，使新陈代谢不受阻碍和破坏，得以正常进行；芦荟、花粉、蜂皇浆都有促进血液循环、刺激内脏、加速新陈代谢的功效。人体新陈代谢正常，也就去除了引起细胞结构和功能异常的内因，使人体细胞组织的结构和功能渐趋正常，也就起到调理由细胞组成的人体各大系统结构和功能的作用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">㈢、提供全面均衡的营养，提高人体免疫力</span></em><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">完美芦荟矿物晶能够全面、均衡地提供人体所需的氨基酸、维生素和矿物质。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>摄取必需的营养素为强化免疫力之本<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>， 芦荟矿物晶能提高人体的免疫力。因为：芦荟矿物晶提供的营养素（<span lang=\"EN-US\">VA</span>等）能保持人体皮肤和内脏粘膜的结构完整，拒挡病毒、病菌于人体组织之外；提供营养素，保证体液中杀菌物质和吞噬细胞的正常产生；使免疫器官发挥正常功能，保存免疫细胞的数量和功能。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">完美芦荟矿物晶针对现代社会环境污染严重，人们饮食中各种维生素和矿物质缺乏或不均衡，而脂肪、碳水化合物过剩等特点。采用<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>消除人体垃圾，补充人体全面、均衡营养<span lang=\"EN-US\">&mdash;</span>既清又补、清补并重<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>的科学保健原理。排除了人体生病的内因（新陈代谢不佳），加强了人体防御外来致病因素侵入的堡垒（免疫力），是现代人保持健康、预防疾病的最佳营养保健品。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">服用方法：取适量芦荟矿物晶，用冷开水冲服。饮后多喝水。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">注意事项：勿用金属杯匙，须用冷开水冲服；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">[</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">食品生产许可证号<span lang=\"EN-US\">]QS4420&nbsp; 0601&nbsp; 0247<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">[</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">卫生许可证号<span lang=\"EN-US\">]GD&middot;FDA</span>健证字<span lang=\"EN-US\">[2005]</span>第<span lang=\"EN-US\">2000S0128</span>号<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></spa