yle=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">人类的食物是多种多样的，以往还没有任何一种食物能提供人体所需的全部营养素。完美公司经过长期的潜心研究，以中国营养学会最新制定的《中国居民膳食营养参考摄入量》为指导依据，通过调配各种物质的用量，使营养餐达到最科学的组合配方。经科学组方而成的完美营养餐是完全营养食品，</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">能提供人体所需的全面的营养素，具有以下保健功能。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:\r\nnormal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">、提供全面均衡的营养</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050\">--</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">完美营养餐含有丰富的氨基酸、维生素、矿物质、功能性油脂和膳食纤维，是真正的完全营养食品。</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">能增强体质，对营养不良、体质单薄以及病后需要调养者、孕妇、乳母、婴幼儿非常适合；能促进少年儿童生长发育，改善记忆；能改善因缺乏相关营养素引起的病症，如营养性贫血、骨质疏松、脚气病等。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:\r\nnormal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">、降血脂、降血压、预防心脑血管疾病</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050\">--</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">大豆含有皂角甙、卵磷脂和亚油酸，螺旋藻中富含的亚油酸和<span lang=\"EN-US\">&gamma;&mdash;</span>亚麻酸，糙米、全麦、玉米、大豆、燕麦所富含的纤维素都具有降血脂的作用；营养餐中丰富的维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>、锌、钙都有使血压下降的作用；</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;\r\nfont-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">经常饮用营养餐能预防动脉硬化和各种心脑血管疾病。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:\r\nnormal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">、降血糖</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050\">--</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">糙米、大豆富含锌，糙米富含铬，糙米、全麦、玉米、大豆、燕麦都含有丰富的纤维素，螺旋藻所富含的<span lang=\"EN-US\">&gamma; &mdash;</span>亚 麻酸 及 锌、 镁、 钾， 南瓜粉所含的南瓜戊糖都有降血糖的功效，因此完美营养餐</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">非常适合糖尿病人饮用。</span></strong><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:\r\nnormal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">4</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">、改善肠胃功能，预防消化道疾病<span lang=\"EN-US\">-</span></span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\ncolor:#00B050\">-</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">完美营养餐中含有丰富的膳食纤维，膳食纤维能清扫肠道、</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">加速排便</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">、减少肠道内的有害菌、增殖有益菌，还能</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">减少肠道对有毒物质的吸收</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">，螺旋藻富含叶绿素、藻蓝素、<span lang=\"EN-US\">&beta;&mdash;</span>胡萝卜素和<span lang=\"EN-US\">&gamma;&mdash;</span>亚麻酸，这些物质具有抗粘膜组织炎症、修补受损伤细胞和恢复正常分泌功能，对</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">预防慢性胃炎与消化道溃疡有显著作用。</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\"><o:p></o:p></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:\r\nnormal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">5</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">、改善睡眠<span lang=\"EN-US\">-</span></span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\ncolor:#00B050\">-</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">燕麦、玉米所含的松果体素，糙米、大豆所含的锌，玉米所含的铜都具有改善睡眠的功效。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:\r\nnormal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">6</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">、延缓衰老</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050\">--</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">大豆所含的大豆皂甙、玉米所含的维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">E</span>及营养餐中所含的维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">&beta;-</span>胡萝卜素、卵磷脂、氨基酸等都抗衰老的作用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">完美营养餐是一种典型的营养保健食品<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span>主要通过营养因素：提供人体所需的营养素和减少人体内过剩的营养素，来保持人体健康，预防疾病；在补充调节人体营养素这方面，完美营养餐的作用是独一无二的，对健康人而言，它是最合适的保健食品之一。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">完美营养餐在加工过程中采用了</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;\r\nfont-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">超微破碎、糊化、低温干燥</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">等先进的物料处理方法， 保证各种营养成分不流失、不被破坏、</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">养而不腻</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">，迎合了我们<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>想吃就吃<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>的需求，而又不必担心热气上火。</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;\r\nfont-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">用热水冲泡的营养餐，闻起来香，看起来靓，喝起来更爽！</span></strong><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><em><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050\">哪些人需要食用完美营养餐？</span></em><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">①</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">脑力劳动者：丰富的维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">B</span>群和微量元素</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">能镇定神经</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">，促进脑细胞的生长；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">②</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">胃口不好、抵抗力弱、发育不良的少年儿童：锌能促进脑垂体分泌生长激素，</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">促进</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">儿童全身尤其是</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">骨骼的成长；</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">③</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">糖尿病患者：糙米胚芽是现有食品中含</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">锌</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">量最高的食物，</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">辅助糖尿病的治疗有惊人的效果；</span></strong><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">④</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">高血压和心脑病患者：大量的不饱和脂肪酸可以</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">分解胆固醇，保护心脏</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">，使高血压降低；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">⑤</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">脚气病和常腰酸背痛人士；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">⑥</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">风湿痛和关节炎患者，以及肝炎患者；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">⑦</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;\r\nfont-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">体质单薄及病后需调养的人士</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">⑧</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;\r\nfont-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">孕妇和乳母、婴幼儿</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">；<b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">⑨</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">时常便秘者；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">⑩</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">性功能减退者；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#00B050\">⑾</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">需减肥者；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#00B050\">⑿</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">贫血者。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">市面有许多类似的营养餐如</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;\r\nfont-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">麦片</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">等含有高糖分，多吃无益，</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050\">会</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;\r\nfont-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">造成儿童蛀牙、肥胖</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">等问题，而完美营养餐则不含一般蔗糖，采用昂贵的对人体有益的果糖配制，即使糖尿病病人吃了也无妨。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">完美营养餐食用方便，用开水冲匀既可，浓淡随意，香味醇厚浓郁，口感绝佳，</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">是全家人理想的完全营养食品。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">[</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">食品生产许可证号<span lang=\"EN-US\">]QS4420 0601 0247<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">[</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">卫生许可证号<span lang=\"EN-US\">]</span>粤卫食证字<span lang=\"EN-US\">[2003]</span>第<span lang=\"EN-US\">2012A02267</span>号<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">[</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">产品标准号<span lang=\"EN-US\">]Q/WMRY0052S</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/1664624524/T2dB__XlxXXXXXXXXX_!!1664624524.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/1664624524/T25Sv_XiFXXXXXXXXX_!!1664624524.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/1664624524/T2RSr_Xi8XXXXXXXXX_!!1664624524.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/1664624524/T28xNTXexeXXXXXXXX_!!1664624524.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/1664624524/T2Y22_XbxaXXXXXXXX_!!1664624524.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/1664624524/T2BIH.XctXXXXXXXXX_!!1664624524.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/1664624524/T2HlP_XktXXXXXXXXX_!!1664624524.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/1664624524/T28PTtXkdaXXXXXXXX_!!1664624524.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/1664624524/T220J4XjRdXXXXXXXX_!!1664624524.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/1664624524/T2EIL.Xb8XXXXXXXXX_!!1664624524.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:44.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:\r\n22.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\ncolor:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">产品问答</span></strong><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:22.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">1、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">问：苯酮尿症是什么病症。为何此患者不可食用营养餐<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:\r\nnormal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">苯酮尿症</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">是一种极少见<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>占万分之一<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>的先天性苯丙氨酸转化酶缺乏而致的代谢性疾病。因营养餐中含阿斯巴甜，阿斯巴甜经分解会产生苯丙氨酸，苯丙氨酸不适合苯酮尿症患者食用，所以苯酮尿症患者不可食用营养餐。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">2、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">问：完美营养餐怎么解释是为补充营养、调节体内代谢、调理肠道而生产的<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：是的。今天对我们来讲，温饱已经不是主要的问题，而是如何吃好，如何享受美味佳肴。很明显，许多人还没有注意到</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">均衡营养的重要性和必要性</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">。我们大多数人都喜欢吃肉，但是人们同时却忽视了对植物膳食的摄入，饱口福的时候忘记了如此的饮食会造成<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>文明病<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>也就是我们通常说的富贵病：高脂血症、高血压、高胆固醇血症、脂肪肝、糖尿病、肥胖症等。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">完美公司经过长期探索研究，以中国营养学会最新制订的</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050\">《中国居民膳食营养摄入量》</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">为依据，研究配制出的营养餐能够让我们更好、更全面、更迅速、更方便地补充营养，调节体内代谢，调理肠道功能。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">3、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">问：完美营养餐的主要成份有哪些功效特点<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：<span lang=\"EN-US\">①</span>螺旋藻<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span></span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">螺旋藻被世界卫生组织确认为<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>人类二十一世纪最佳保健品<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>，</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">也是世界上广泛推行的优良食品。螺旋藻是世界上最古老的生物种之一，从地球开始形成时就有了螺旋藻的存在，距今已有二十亿年的生命历史。它富含多种生理活性物质和人体必需的营养元素，而且含量比较均衡。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">②</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">糙米胚芽<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span>人们日常生活中，食物讲究精制、好吃，但许多营养却在精制与好吃中丧失了。比如大米经过精心加工，人们将加工去掉的糠层和胚芽，都给了鸡、鸭、禽畜作饲料，而自己吃的是剩余的、没有多少营养的精白米。研究表明，一粒稻米由三部分组成：第一是胚乳，它占了一粒米体积的<span lang=\"EN-US\">92%</span>；第二是糠层，占<span lang=\"EN-US\">5%</span>，第三是胚芽，只占<span lang=\"EN-US\">3%</span>。但从营养方面来看恰恰相反，也就是</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\ncolor:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">只占<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>％体积的胚芽，其所含的营养成分是整粒米的<span lang=\"EN-US\">70</span>％。</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">美国食品与药物管理局对糙米的成份作了分析，证实了糙米能提供人体内所需的矿物质，如：锌、铁、银、磷等，还有蛋白质、叶酸和多种维生素。我们的营养餐中不只含有糙米胚芽，而且还含有其它纯天然的谷类、豆类精华。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">③</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">莲子、薏仁、黑米、燕麦等<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span>完美营养餐中还含有莲子、薏仁、黑米、糙米、大豆蛋白粉、南瓜粉、燕麦等多种营养价值特别高的物质。也许有人会问，上面这些东西，在市面上随便就能买到、有什么特别之处呢<span lang=\"EN-US\">?</span>很简单，人类的食物是多种多样的，而各种食物所含的营养成分不同，任何一种食物都不能全面的提供人体所需的全部营养素，必须由多种食物组合才能满足人体对各种营养的需求，达到合理供给，保持人体健康。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">4、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">问：完美营养餐的加工方法有什么独特之处<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：采用了超微破碎、糊化和低温干燥等先进的物料处理方法，保证了各种营养成份不流失、不被破坏，温而不燥，不必担心热气上火。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">5、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">问：哪些类型的人需要服用完美营养餐<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：<span lang=\"EN-US\">①</span>脑力劳动者；<span lang=\"EN-US\">②</span>高血压、高血脂、高胆固醇血症患者；<span lang=\"EN-US\">③</span>动脉硬化、心脏病患者；<span lang=\"EN-US\">④</span>糖尿病患者、风湿病、脚气病和肝类患者；<span lang=\"EN-US\">⑤</span>需要调养的人。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">实际上完美营养餐适应的人群非常广泛，无论男女老少都适用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">6、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">问：</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;\r\nfont-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">怎样服<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>食<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>用完美营养餐<span lang=\"EN-US\">?</span></span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：完美营养餐的食用方法简单方便，不用烹煮、用热开水冲匀后即可食用，可按照个人口味随意调配，是理想的营养食品。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">7、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">问：山西地区反映罐装完美营养餐是否新配方？如是，为何未注明<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：是新配方。为减少印刷成本。即减少顾客负担，我们暂还没有修改罐体的印刷。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">8、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">问：完美营养餐与市场出售的麦片有何不同？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：麦片之类的营养餐都是麦类饮品，且均含有较高的糖份，多吃无益，会造成蛀牙、肥胖等问题。完美营养餐是谷类营养品，不含蔗糖，而是采用价值昂贵但对人体非常有益的果糖配制而成，营养丰富，即使是糖尿病者吃了也无妨。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">9、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">问：为什么不干脆吃糙米呢？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：首先，</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;\r\nfont-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">糙米本身很粗糙，吃了不易消化</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">，它的营养成份也难于直接被吸收；其次，味道也难吃，难以下咽，不适宜大众口味。因此完美营养餐是最佳的选择。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">10、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">问：完美营养餐还有什么成份，有何用途？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：新添加的牛磺酸、硫酸锌、酒石酸胆碱和磷酸氢二钾，能促进脑垂体分泌生长激素，促进儿童全身尤其是脑部的发育。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">11、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">问：完美营养餐在一天中什么时候喝效果最好？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：随时都可以，只要你觉得肚子饿或需要补充营养。此外，完美营养餐有小袋装，对出差或工作繁忙者十分方便。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">12、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">问：为什么营养要均衡的吸收？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：一个人的内在健康水准之高低，从营养均衡的角度讲是由一种或几种最缺乏的营养物质<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span></span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">健康决定因素</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">所决定的，如果补足这种或几种<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>健康决定因素<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>，他的健康水平就可以登上一个新的台阶。<span lang=\"EN-US\"> &ldquo;</span>完美营养餐<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>不是常规意义上的几种营养物质的拼凑组合。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>完美营养餐<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>对每种单一营养素进行有针对性地筛选和科学配合。同时更重要的是，每一营养素在人体消化吸收等复杂的生化过程中，发生非常重要的相互协同促进功效。这种</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">各营养素的相互作用力</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">，较单一营养元素的摄取，在更好地吸收利用、更强的保健价值方面具有特殊意义。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">13、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">问：</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">营养餐对<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>营养缺失<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>症的作用</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">？孕妇可否食用？营养缺乏是否会导致胎儿兔唇？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">①</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">营养餐可以帮助补充<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>营养缺失<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>症。但在推介中应注意以下说法：营养餐只是补充人体正常生理代谢中所缺乏的营养而不是提供全部营养所需。<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>因每个人的日常饮食和生活习惯，无法做正确的标准<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">②</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;\r\nfont-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">孕妇可以吃营养餐</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">③</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">导致胎儿兔唇的因素很多，即使营养不缺乏也有可能产生；营养缺失除了会引起胎儿兔唇之外，还会造成很多其它疾病。因此许多人都需要补充营养。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">14、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">问：高纤乐、营养餐中的阿斯巴甜和果糖有何区别？糖尿病人可否服用高纤乐、营养餐？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：果糖是一种单糖。我们的营养餐和高纤乐中所含的阿斯巴甜是一种低热量甜味剂，食用后便会分解为蛋白质成分，可被人体吸收、消化及正常代谢，所以对患有糖尿病的人可食用，且安全。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">15、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">营养餐中的色、香、味与完美餐有何不同？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：营养餐是经过糊化处理，口感很温淳，可以最大限度地将营养成份保存下来，完美餐是经过膨化处理，在口感上比较燥热，营养餐色、香、味都较完美餐好。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">16、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">问：营养餐中是否含有完美餐中的四种补脑成份？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：营养餐中不再含有完美餐的四种补脑成份，但在营养餐的各种原料中均有补脑成份。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">17、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">问：完美产品用什么<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>糖<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>能详细了解一下吗？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：如果你问一个孩子，喜欢吃<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>糖<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>吗？他肯定会睁着大眼睛微笑着给你一个肯定的回答。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>糖<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>代表着喜庆、欢乐和享受，几乎没有人会不喜欢它。然而</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">您真正了解<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>糖<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>吗？</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">您知道</span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;\r\nfont-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">&ldquo;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">蔗糖<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>吃多了会</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">有哪些害处吗？</span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">①</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">引起热量过剩；<span lang=\"EN-US\">②</span>造成龋齿。</span></strong><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\"><br />\r\n</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">可诱人的甜味实在让人难以拒绝。而且许多食品如果没有了甜甜的味道可能就没有人想吃了。怎么办呢？办法是肯定有的。下面给大家介绍的就是<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>糖<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>系列中更加优秀的两位成员<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span></span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">&ldquo;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">果糖<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>和<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>阿斯巴甜<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">你喜欢水果中的甜味吗<span lang=\"EN-US\">?</span>其实水果中存在的<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>糖<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>主要就是<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>果糖<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>，它的甜度是<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>蔗糖<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>的<span lang=\"EN-US\">1.8</span>倍，现代工艺从各种原料中提取的果糖已在食品中得到广泛利用，添加<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>果糖<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>与添加<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>蔗糖<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>相比，在不降低产品甜度的情况下、可减少产品的热量；<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>果糖<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>不会创造口腔微生物生长的合适环境，不易造成龋齿；<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>果糖<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>对胰岛素水平和血糖值的影响非常小。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>阿斯巴甜<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>是目前在食品、保健食品中使用范围极为广泛的一种新型甜味剂，甜味纯正，</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">它的甜度是蔗糖的<span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span>倍</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">，故只需少量就可以达到所希望的甜度，因而可大大降低产品中的热值。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>阿斯巴甜<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>自<span lang=\"EN-US\">1991</span>年被美国食品和药物管理局<span lang=\"EN-US\">(FDA)</span>核准通过后，目前已被世界各地<span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span>多个国家及多个国际权威组织认可，其中包括世界卫生组织<span lang=\"EN-US\">(WHO)</span>、美国、加拿大糖尿病协会等。在美国和法国高甜度合成甜味剂市场上它分别占到<span lang=\"EN-US\">70%</span>和<span lang=\"EN-US\">80%</span>。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>阿斯巴甜<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>的分解物是氨基酸，代谢时与胰岛素有关，是糖尿病人的安全食品，同时也不会致龋。但由于代谢产物之一为<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>苯丙氨酸<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>，故<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>苯丙酮尿症<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>患者需慎用。在此需要说明的是，</span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">&ldquo;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">苯丙酮尿症<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>主要是<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>个月至<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>岁小儿发病</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">，发病率极低，在中国约为<span lang=\"EN-US\">1/16500</span>，为遗传性疾病。随着儿童生长发育，病症会自然痊愈。所以<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>阿斯巴甜<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>仍是目前市场上先进和优秀的甜味剂。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"marginleft\" style=\"margin-left: 14px; font-family: Simsun;\">\r\n<div id=\"txt_ulli\" style=\"width: 706px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span id=\"Label_Content\"> </span></div>\r\n</div>', 'images/201305/thumb_img/197_thumb_G_1369843125173.png', 'images/201305/goods_img/197_G_1369843125233.jpg', 'images/201305/source_img/197_G_1369843125982.png', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1369456004', '86', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1371181178', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '');
