ont-kerning:\r\n0pt\">产品规格：<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>克<span lang=\"EN-US\">&times;30</span>袋<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:黑体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">产品价格：￥<span lang=\"EN-US\">213<o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 24pt; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312, serif; color: rgb(255, 204, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span><img src=\"http://www.perfect99.com/product_pic/BigImages/FA30.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 24pt; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312, serif; color: rgb(255, 204, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 22pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">改善消化、清理血液、洁净泌尿<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:154.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:7.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 22pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;----</span><span style=\"font-size: 22pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">完美低聚果糖沙棘茶</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">主要成份：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">①沙棘粉<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>选用大西北荒漠中的高原圣果<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span>沙棘为主要原料；②红茶粉<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>选用高原无污染的新茶为原料；<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">产品功效：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">一、改善消化系统<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>增加双歧杆菌数量，促进大肠蠕动，提高新陈代谢，改善营养吸收功能，消除体内各种毒素，对肠炎、结肠炎有特效。菊粉经酶转化后形成<span lang=\"EN-US\">IOS</span>，而<span lang=\"EN-US\">IOS</span>是双歧杆菌的高效增殖因子，能活化肠道内的双歧杆菌并促进其生长繁殖，双岐杆菌是人体肠道内的有益菌群，其数量的多少直接反应人体的健康状况，它可以减少肠道有害细菌（如痢疾细菌、霍乱细菌等）的数量，增强人体免疫力，并且能在人体肠道内合成<span lang=\"EN-US\">B</span>族维生素，维护人体神经系统的正常运作。双岐杆菌与人是一种共生的关系（共生是指两种或两种以上生物互利、互惠的生存方式），其生长繁殖贯穿于人的整个生命历程。新生婴儿<span lang=\"EN-US\">2-3</span>天后粪便中便可发现双歧杆菌，<span lang=\"EN-US\">4-5</span>天后双歧杆菌占肠道细菌的绝大部分；随着年龄的增长，双歧杆菌的数量逐渐减少；体质虚弱者，双歧杆菌的存在量很少；在临死的人的肠道中，根本不存在双歧杆菌。双歧杆菌有很强的保健作用，近二十年来医学专家们对这类菌进行了比较详细的研究，特别是近几年随着人们保健意识的增强，对双歧杆菌的利用也越来越多。双歧杆菌对胃炎、腹泻、慢性痢疾、消化不良、免疫力下降、解毒护肝、痔疮、便秘等肠胃道疾病有明显的调理作用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">二、清洁循环系统<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>沙棘黄酮、&beta;<span lang=\"EN-US\">-</span>谷固醇、甜菜碱、茶多酚、菊粉等多种活性物质具有降低血清胆固醇含量、清除血管壁上的沉积物、抑制血小板过度聚集、提高高密度脂蛋白含量、增加血红蛋白、软化血管、恢复血管弹性、增大血流量、增加对大脑的供血能力、调节血脂代谢等作用。因此对心脑血管疾病有很好的辅助治疗作用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">三、洁净沁尿系统<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>通过补充甘露醇，促进体内多余水份及时排出，防止污垢在体内沉积，对肾脏、尿路感染、前列腺等有较高的洁净功能。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">服用方法：用于保健<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span>每天<span lang=\"EN-US\">1-2</span>包；用于治疗康复<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span>每天<span lang=\"EN-US\">3-4</span>包。将<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>包（<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>克）沙棘茶渗入<span lang=\"EN-US\">200ml</span>温开水或<span lang=\"EN-US\">150ml</span>冷水中搅拌溶解后即可饮用。也可根据个人喜好增减用量，浓淡随意。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">注：肠道功能不佳者，在服用初期，可能感觉病灶处有较明显的好转反应，宜从少量服起。在服用沙棘茶期间，应停用抗生素药物，否则肠道内的有益菌将难以增殖，严重影响产品功效。老年人和曾经长期服用或注射抗生素者，肠道内有益菌数量少，如能在服用沙棘茶的同时，饮用酸奶、乳酸菌饮料等乳酸发酵食品，将有利于在短期内大量增殖肠道有益菌群数量，使保健功效更为显著。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:44.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 22pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">产 品 问 答<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">、问：沙棘茶有无含动物激素<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">答：沙棘茶中不但不含有动物激素，更不含动物性原料，吃素的朋友可放心食用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;2</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">、问：喝了矿物晶再喝健怕茶会影响效果吗<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">答：不会。因为健恰茶把身体里的内环境清理后，使得我们更容易把矿物晶里的矿物质吸收，达到更好的效果。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">、问：沙棘茶是不是有大量的双歧杆菌<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">答：不是，沙棘茶里有菊粉，能倍增我们身体内的有益菌<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>双歧杆菌<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>，使我们的免疫力增强。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;4</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">、问：沙棘茶对人体健康起到什么好处<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">答：因沙棘茶中含有沙棘粉、菊粉，这些原料对人体有以下用：<span lang=\"EN-US\">a</span>、能改善消化系统；<span lang=\"EN-US\">b</span>、清理循环系统；<span lang=\"EN-US\">c</span>、洁净泌尿系统。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">5</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">、问：沙棘茶有降低血压作用，低血压人士可否饮用<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">答：完全可以，沙棘茶是天然健康保健食品，降压主要是降低血清胆固醇和甘油三脂的含量，所以任何人士可放心饮用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">6</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">、问：为什么强调沙棘茶不含糖分<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">答：因为沙棘茶要天天喝，经常喝，如含糖份易引起龋牙。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;7</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">、问：沙棘茶的主要成份是什么<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">答：它主要包含有红茶粉、沙棘粉、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>、菊粉含量高。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">8</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">、问：沙棘茶可以用热开水来冲调吗<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">答：可以。但是我们不提倡这样用，最好是用温开水来冲调，因为这样可以充分保护茶中的维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>，不会变得很酸，保持茶的天然味道和一流的口感。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">9</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">、问：糖尿病及肥胖患者可以喝沙棘茶吗<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">答：可以。沙棘茶所提供的能量值很低，最大限度地满足了那些喜爱甜品而又担心发胖者的要求，也不会引起血糖值的升高，故可供糖尿病人食用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">10</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">、问：客户反映服了沙棘茶后反应很大，连续几天拉肚子，有的感觉牙齿酸，不敢用力吃东西．请问这是否正常反应<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">答：肠胃不好的人或吃东西很杂的人<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>肉类吃多等<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>，服用沙棘茶，特别是初次服用沙棘茶反应是比较强烈，比如：轻微腹泻、排便次数多、排气多都是正常。这属于沙棘茶对人体调整的第一步。如反应过于强烈，可减少用量，每日<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>包，等适之后慢慢增大用量，一般来说，这段时间为<span lang=\"EN-US\">3--5</span>天，牙齿酸不是正常反应，如果顾客一天吃上十几包倒是会牙齿酸。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">11</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">、问：沙棘茶的第一特点是可以降低血压，一般高血压病人需服几盒可达到效果，可否连续服用<span lang=\"EN-US\">3--4</span>包，还是分开服<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">答：高血压服用沙棘茶时，最好是分开服用。不要一次服<span lang=\"EN-US\">3--4</span>包，降血脂、血压一般连续服用<span lang=\"EN-US\">25--30</span>天可见效果。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">12</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">、问：一般调理泌尿系统感染的，可以服用沙棘茶吗<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">答：泌尿系统感染，沙棘茶没有调理的作用，沙棘茶主要是可以防止储留体内的水份流失，并可防止尿路结石等。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">13</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">、沙棘茶中菊粉是什么性质<span lang=\"EN-US\">?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">答：沙棘茶中的菊粉不是菊花中的东西，也与菊花无任何关系，它是植物菊苣的茎中提取的一种具备保健作用的物质，能极有效的改善人的消化系统与循环系统。清除体内的各种垃圾，使人体处于一种健康的状态。其主要作用是：①使体内双歧杆菌迅速增加，抑制有害菌的生长；②促进体内维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">B</span>群的合成；③降低胆固醇及血压等</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 22pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"marginleft\" style=\"margin-left: 14px; font-family: Simsun;\">\r\n<div id=\"txt_ulli\" style=\"width: 706px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span id=\"Label_Content\"> </span></div>\r\n</div>', 'images/201306/thumb_img/200_thumb_G_1370064460401.gif', 'images/201306/goods_img/200_G_1370064460510.jpg', 'images/201306/source_img/200_G_1370064460040.gif', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1369456004', '83', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1371175319', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '');
