e:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;\r\ncolor:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">低聚果糖是指</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nsimsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">～</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">个果糖基为链节，以一个葡萄糖基为链的端基，以果糖基</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">&rarr;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">果糖连接键为主体骨架连结形成的碳水化合物。即是指</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">～</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">个果糖基以</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">&beta;-2</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">键连接在蔗糖的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">D-</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">果糖基上而形成的蔗果三糖（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">GF2</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">）、蔗果四糖（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">GF3</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">）、蔗果五糖（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">GF4</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">）和蔗果六糖（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">GF5</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">）的混合物。商品低聚果糖一般还含有少量蔗糖、果糖、葡萄糖。（参考目前正在制定中的国家标准中的定义）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">天然活性物质</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;\r\ncolor:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">低聚果糖是一种天然活性物质。甜度为蔗糖的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">0.3-0.6</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">倍。既保持了蔗糖的纯正甜味性质，又比蔗糖甜味清爽。是具有调节肠道菌群，增殖双歧杆菌，促进钙的吸收，调节血脂，免疫调节，抗龋齿等保健功能的新型甜味剂，被誉为继抗生素时代后最具潜力的新一代添加剂</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">促生物质；在法国被称为原生素（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">PPE</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">），已在乳制品、乳酸菌饮料、固体饮料、糖果、饼干、面包、果冻、泠饮等多种食品中应用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">养生功效</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;\r\ncolor:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">低聚果糖除具有一般功能性低聚糖的物理化学性质外，最引人注目的生理特性是它能明显改善肠道内微生物种群比例，它是肠内双歧杆菌的活化增殖因子，可减少和抑制肠内腐败物质的产生，抑制有害细菌的生长，调节肠道内平衡；能促进微量元素铁、钙的吸收与利用，以防止骨质疏松症；可减少肝脏毒素，能在肠中生成抗癌的有机酸，有显著的防癌功能；且口味纯正香甜可口，具有类似脂肪的香味和爽口的滑腻感。近几年低聚果糖的产品风靡日、欧、美等保健品市场。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;\r\ncolor:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">糖浆为无色或淡黄色、透明粘稠液体，带低聚果糖清香，甜味柔和清爽，无异味，无外来杂质。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;\r\ncolor:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">糖粉为白色或微黄色无定型粉末（颗粒为白色或微黄色无定型颗粒），甜味柔和清爽，带低聚果糖清香，无异味，无外来杂质。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><u><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">六大功效</span></u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">1. </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">低热能值，由于低聚果糖不能被人体直接消化吸收，只能被肠道细菌吸收利用，故其热值低，不会导致肥胖，间接也有减肥作用。对糖尿病患者来说也是一种良好的甜味剂。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">2. </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">由于其不能被口腔细菌</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">指突变链球菌</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">Smutans)</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">利用，因而具有防龋齿作用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">3. </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nsimsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">对肠道益菌的增殖作用。低聚果糖对肠道中有益菌群如双岐杆菌、乳酸杆菌等有选择性增殖作用，使有益菌群在肠道中占有优势，抑制有害菌的生长，减少有毒物质</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">如内毒素、氨类等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">的形成，对肠粘膜细胞和肝具有保护作用，从而防止病变肠癌的发生，增强机体免疫力。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">4. </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nsimsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">可降低血清中胆固醇和甘油三酯的含量。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">5. </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nsimsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">促进营养的吸收，尤其是钙的吸收。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nsimsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">6. </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">防治腹泄和便秘。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">低聚果糖的属性与作用机理</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nsimsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">　　低聚果糖是一种水溶性膳食纤维，长期服用可以降低血清胆固醇，改善脂质代谢，经动物和人体实验证实。低聚果糖具有如下生理功能：为双歧杆菌等有益菌所利用，即只增殖</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">10</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">～</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">100</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">倍，时双歧杆菌（致病菌），具有双向调节之功效。人体摄入低聚果糖后，体内有益菌群双歧杆菌数量可抑制外源致病菌和肠内固有腐败细菌如沙门氏菌等生长繁殖，减少肠内腐败物质的生长和积累，促进肠道蠕动，防止便秘和腹泻。低聚果糖是一种优良的水溶性膳食纤维，能有效降低血清胆固醇、甘油三脂、游离脂肪酸的数量，对于因血脂高而引起的高血压、动脉硬化等一系列心血管疾病有较好的改善作用。低聚果糖在大肠内被细菌发酵生成</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">L</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">－乳酸，可以溶解钙、镁、铁等矿物质，促进</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nsimsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">人体对矿物质的吸收。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nsimsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">　　实验证实，低聚果糖促进钙的吸收率达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">70.8</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">％。因此，低聚果糖可以促进生长发育和防止骨质疏松症。同时还可促进维生素</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">B1</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">B2</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">B3</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">B6</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">B12</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">及叶酸的自然形成，从而提高人体新陈代谢水平，提高免疫力和抗病力。预防及改善由于体内毒而引起的皮肤性疾病，可防止面疮、黑斑、雀斑，青春痘、老人斑，使皮肤亮丽、老化减缓。双歧杆菌吸收低聚果糖后，迅速增殖，抑制大肠杆菌、沙门氏菌和梭状芽胞杆菌等腐败菌发生作用，减少毒性代谢物（如吲哚、亚硝基氨）的生成，同时迅速将毒性代谢物排出体外，减轻肝脏负担，起到保护肝脏的作用，预防各种慢性疾病、健肠等作用明显，低聚果糖极少会被消化道中的胃酸和酶分解，极难被人体吸收。据测定，低聚果糖的热值为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">1.5Kcal/g</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">以下</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">,</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">而蔗糖热值为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">4.6Kcal/g,</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">因此摄入低聚果糖后</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">,</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;\r\ncolor:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">不会引起肥胖</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">,</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nsimsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">是理想的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">,</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">低热值的功能性甜味剂</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">.</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">低聚果糖不能被突变链球菌利用生成不溶性葡聚糖而提供口腔微生物沉积</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">\\</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">产酸和腐蚀的场所</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">牙垢</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#92D050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">),</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">因此可以防止龋齿。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:red;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">健康美丽的秘密　肠道年轻有活力</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align=\"center\">\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"width:100.0%;border-collapse:collapse;mso-yfti-tbllook:1184;mso-padding-alt:\r\n    0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;\r\n            mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n            simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">由于现代人的饮食过于精细，导致越来越多的人都有难以启齿的困扰</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\n            font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\n            mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">便秘，需要借助各种</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\n            font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\n            mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">外力</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\n            font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\n            mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">，才能将体内宿便排出去。宿便长期停留肠内，积蓄的毒素会破坏肠壁，再经由毛细血管进入体内循环，从而引出皮肤粗糙、肩膀酸痛、烦躁、易疲劳等表现</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\n            font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\n            mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">这便是曾获诺贝尔医学奖的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\n            font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\n            mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">自体中毒</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\n            font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\n            mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">说。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;\r\n            mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n            simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">食物进入胃内，经由胃酸和各种酶的分解处理，化成便于消化的粥状进入小肠，再由小肠内的各种消化液，将脂肪、淀粉和蛋白质等分解成细小分子进入毛细血管，剩余部分再进入大肠，由大肠吸收掉其中的水分，当储存到一定量时，则给大脑发出信号产生便意，从而排出体外。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n            宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n            simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\n            mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\">当肠动力发生改变，如蠕动过快，使营养吸收不全甚至不吸收，则会导致腹泻；而蠕动过慢，使食物残渣长时间在体内残留，水分被吸干，则会产生便秘。不管哪一种，都标示着肠内有害细菌增加，如果不加以改善，则会导致肠道老化，无法正常完成吸收与排泄的使命。而肠道老化，则进一步影响肠动力，从而形成恶性循环。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n            宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;\r\n            mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n            simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">测测看，你的肠道老了吗？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n            宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;\r\n            mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n            simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">比起实际年龄，你的肠道老了吗？对照下面的情况，如果有三条以上符合，就预示着你的肠道在变老。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n            宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n            宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\">☆</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\n            mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\n            minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\n            color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">屁很臭</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\n            font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\"> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\n            font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\n            mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">☆</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;\r\n            mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n            simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">大便黑</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\n            minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">☆</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;\r\n            mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n            simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">大便恶臭</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\n            minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">☆</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;\r\n            mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n            simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">大便干硬或呈泥状</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\n            minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">☆</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;\r\n            mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n            simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">连续便秘好几天</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\n            minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">☆</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;\r\n            mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n            simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">经常腹胀</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\n            minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">☆</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;\r\n            mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n            simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">容易生粉刺、长脓包</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\n            minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">☆</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;\r\n            mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n            simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">皮肤粗糙，不易上妆</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n            宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;\r\n            mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n            simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">肠道年轻方程式</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n            宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;\r\n            mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n            simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">随着年龄的增长，肠道内的有益菌越来越少，有害菌则增多。而精米精面、鱼肉蛋奶摄入过多，以及久坐、熬夜、运动少等不良的生活方式，也使现代人体内有害菌增多，肠道提前步入</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\n            font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\n            mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">老龄化</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\n            font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\n            mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">。如何才能减缓肠道变老的脚步？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n            宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;\r\n            mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n            simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">帮助</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;\r\n            mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n            simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">益生菌＋低聚果糖＋膳食纤维</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">――――&rarr;</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n            13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n            宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;\r\n            mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">年轻肠道</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;\r\n            mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n            simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">获得</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n            宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;\r\n            mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n            simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">益生菌：直接补充含益生菌的食品，如酸奶、乳酪、益生菌胶囊等，直接植入有益菌群，使其在肠道内繁殖，保持肠道年轻的活力。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n            宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;\r\n            mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n            simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">低聚果糖：对肠道中有益菌群如双歧杆菌等有选择性增殖作用，使有益菌群在肠道中占有优势，抑制有害菌的生长，减少体内毒素的产生，能恢复肠道生态平衡，促进肠道蠕动，改善腹泄和便秘。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n            宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;\r\n            mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n            simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">活立多健肠口服液　我要</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\n            font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\n            mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">肠</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n            13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\n            mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\n            minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\n            color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">运动</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n            13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\n            mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;\r\n            mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n            simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">活立多健肠口服液是以低聚果糖为主要原料制成的保健食品，经功能试验证明，具有改善胃肠道功能（润肠通便）的保健功能。初次服用可能会产生气涨、排气增多和轻泻，此属排除肠内积宿腐败有害物的正常现象。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n            宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;\r\n            mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n            simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">一生糖　享用一生的健康甜蜜</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n            宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;\r\n            mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n            simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">活立多牌一生糖是通过现代生物工程技术精制而成的益生元，长期食用，有益于身体健康。一生糖不但甘甜可口，更是肠道有益菌双歧杆菌最爱吃的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\n            font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\n            mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">专用营养餐</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\n            font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\n            mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">。它低热量，能提供人体所必需的营养，还能促进和改善人体生理机能，帮助维护肠道微生态的平衡；它是一种健康糖、绿色糖、功能糖，更是应该一生都享用的保健糖。</span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n            宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;\r\n            mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n            simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">膳食纤维：膳食纤维像一把</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\n            font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\n            mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">大扫帚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\n            font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\n            mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">，全面清洁肠道内环境，使有害菌无</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\n            font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\n            mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">立足之地</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\n            font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\n            mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:#92D050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">。水溶性纤维可携带胆固醇、胆汁酸等，将其排出体外，使脂肪代谢后的废物、尿素等能及时清除；而不溶性纤维则可促使胃肠蠕动，增加肠动力，有助于体内有益菌的增加。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n            宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#92D050;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;\r\n            mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n            simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">高纤乐：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\n            font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\n            mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n            宋体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">肠</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n            13.5pt;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\n            mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\n            minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;mso-b', 'images/201306/thumb_img/203_thumb_G_1370058295682.gif', 'images/201306/goods_img/203_G_1370058295805.jpg', 'images/201306/source_img/203_G_1370058295756.gif', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1369456004', '80', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1371165935', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '');
