t-kerning:\r\n0pt\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">完美牌健扬胶囊<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>是以黄精提取物、巴戟天提取物、枸杞子提取物、灵芝提取物、制何首乌提取物、三七提取物为主要原料、以传统中医理论为指导，结合现代医学方法科学配制而成的保健食品。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">经功能试验证明，<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>完美牌健扬胶囊<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>针对人体持续疲劳引发的记忆力减退、头晕耳鸣、失眠多梦、肌肉酸痛、性功能减退、烦躁易怒、全身乏力等<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>亚健康<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>现象，具有缓解体力疲劳的保健功能。长期食用可增强体魄，让您的生活充满激情！<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:22.0pt;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">(</span></u></b><b><u><span style=\"font-size:22.0pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">完美</span></u></b><b><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:22.0pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">)</span></u></b><b><u><span style=\"font-size:22.0pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">健扬胶囊</span></u></b><b><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:22.0pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">--</span></u></b><b><u><span style=\"font-size:22.0pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">男宝提高男性性功能</span></u></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:22.0pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">在竞争压力异常激烈的当今社会，人们的疲劳感正在肆意蔓延，时下最流行的问候语由</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">20</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">年前的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:red;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">吃了吗？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">变成了如今的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">吃力吗？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">。我们每天都在为幸福美好的生活打拼，常年不知疲倦地工作，但是，你是否知道疾病往往就住在疲劳的隔壁呢？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">疲劳就好比没有军队的国家一样极易让人土崩瓦解，当人体失去防御能力时，疾病就如非法入侵者一样乘虚而入</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&hellip;&hellip;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">因此，第一时间恢复体力，缓解疲劳是时下保健养生的当务之急。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">完美牌健扬胶囊由黄精、巴戟天、灵芝、枸杞等多种名贵中药经科学配伍，运用现代先进工艺研制而成，经功能测试证明，具有补气益肾、强健筋骨、补益精血、缓解体力疲劳等功效。结合传统中医中药相互提携、相辅相成的经典理论，帮助解决现代人的亚健康状态，尽显我国中医中药的博大精深</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&hellip;&hellip;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">完美牌健扬胶囊让您无论何时何地都能保持充沛的体力，享受健康，尽情绽放活力！<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">黄精的功效：</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">黄精以根茎入药。具有补气养阴，健脾，润肺，益肾功能。用于治疗脾胃虚弱，体倦乏力，口干食少，肺虚燥咳，气血不足，内热消渴等症。对于糖尿病很有疗效。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">中药治脾胃虚弱，体倦乏力，食欲不振，心悸，气短，肺虚燥咳，津伤口渴，消渴病，肾虚精亏，腰膝酸软；外用治脚癣。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">蒙药冶身体虚弱，胃寒，消化不良，食积，食泻，肾寒，滑精，阳痿，头晕目眩，寒性</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">希日乌素</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:red;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">病，腰腿痛，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">巴达干</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">病。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">黄精的药理作用：</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、抗病原微生物作用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、对血糖过高呈显著抑制作用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、抗疲劳作用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、抗氧化作用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、延缓衰老作用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、止血作用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、对心血管作用：明显增加麻醉犬冠脉流量；对垂体后叶素引起的兔心肌缺血有对抗作用，对抗垂体后叶素引起的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">T</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">波增高，促进</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:red;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">T</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">波异常提前恢复；可增强对缺氧的耐受力。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">8</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、抗病毒作用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">枸杞子的功效：</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">补肾益精，养肝明目，补血安神，生津止渴，润肺止咳。治肝肾阴亏，腰膝酸软，头晕，目眩，目昏多泪，虚劳咳嗽，消渴，遗精。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">枸杞子的作用：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">抗脂肪肝的作用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">拟胆碱样作用<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">枸杞虽然具有很好的滋补和治疗作用，但也不是所有的人都适合服用的。由于它温热身体的效果相当强，正在感冒发烧、身体有炎症、腹泻的人最好别吃<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">最适合吃枸杞的是体质虚弱、抵抗力差的人。而且，一定要长期坚持，每天吃一点，才能见效。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">巴戟天</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">功效：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">补肾阳，壮筋骨，祛风湿。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">治阳痿，少腹冷痛，小便不禁，子宫虚冷，风寒湿痹，腰膝酸痛。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:45.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">①<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">《本经》：主大风邪气，阴痿不起，强筋骨，安五脏，补中增志益气。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:45.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">②<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">《别录》：疗头面游风，小腹及阴中相引痛，下气，补五劳，益精。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:45.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">③<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">《药性论》：治男子梦交泄精，强阴，除头面中风，主下气，大风血癞。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:45.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">④<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">《日华子本草》：安五脏，定心气，除一切风。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">疗水肿。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:45.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">⑤<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">《纲目》：治脚气，去风疾，补血海。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:45.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">⑥<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">《本草求原》：化痰，治嗽喘，眩晕，泄泻，食少。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:45.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">⑦<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">广州部队《常用中草药手册》：补肾壮阳，强筋骨，祛风湿。治肾虚腰脚无力，痿痹瘫痪，风湿骨痛，神经衰弱，阳萎遗精，早泄，失眠；妇女不育。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:45.0pt;text-indent:0cm;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:45.0pt;text-indent:0cm;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">灵芝的功效：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:42.75pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">（1）<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">治慢性支气管炎。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:42.75pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">（2）<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">治支气管哮喘。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:42.75pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">（3）<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">治白细胞减少症。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:42.75pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">（4）<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">治疗冠心病。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:42.75pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">（5）<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">治疗心律失常。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:42.75pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">（6）<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">治急性病毒性肝炎，比传统的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">护肝</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:red;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">药物疗效好。此外，还用于治疗萎缩性胃炎，恶性肿瘤等。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:42.75pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">（7）<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">抗神经衰弱。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:42.75pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">（8）<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">治疗糖尿病。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">灵芝的作用：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1,</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">抗肿瘤作用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:red;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp; 2,</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">保肝解毒作用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:red;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp; 3,</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">对心血管系统的作用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:red;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp; 4,</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">抗衰老作用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:red;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp; 5,</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">抗神经衰弱作用 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:red;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">6,</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">治疗高血压</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">&nbsp; 7,</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">治疗糖尿病</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 8,</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">对慢性支气管炎</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">,</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">支气管哮喘作用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp; 9,</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">抗过敏作用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:red;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp; 10,</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">美容作用</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:黑体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<div class=\"marginleft\" style=\"margin-left: 14px; font-family: Simsun;\">\r\n<div id=\"txt_ulli\" style=\"width: 706px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span id=\"Label_Content\"> </span></div>\r\n</div>', 'images/201306/thumb_img/204_thumb_G_1370058183590.gif', 'images/201306/goods_img/204_G_1370058183804.jpg', 'images/201306/source_img/204_G_1370058183447.gif', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1369456004', '79', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1371163406', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '');
