ily:黑体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">产品价格：￥<span lang=\"EN-US\">285</span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"http://www.perfect99.com/product_pic/BigImages/BC.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;mso-themecolor:accent2;\r\nmso-themetint:153\">云想衣裳花想容<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>，每个女人都有一个白雪公主般美丽的梦，梦想着能拥有珍珠般完美无暇、水嫩透白、滑如凝脂的肌肤<span lang=\"EN-US\">&hellip;&hellip;</span>但时光给我们沉淀，也给我们带来斑驳痕迹，拿什么来对抗这似水年华？让美丽的肌肤了无岁月之痕，让您不做<span lang=\"EN-US\"> &ldquo;</span>斑点女人<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent2;mso-themetint:153\">完美牌丹参阿胶珍珠胶囊就能帮您拒绝<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>斑点<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>困扰，打造白净无暇的<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>完美肌肤<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>！<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent2;mso-themetint:153\">本品蕴含珍珠、乌骨鸡、丹参、阿胶、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">E</span>等天然精华，具有祛除黄褐斑、通便的保健功能，在您轻松祛斑的同时还能让您摆脱便秘的困扰！<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent2;mso-themetint:153\">完美牌丹参阿胶珍珠胶囊，是您美丽肌肤的秘密武器，让美容的大敌斑斑点点、便秘通通下班！让您轻松做个完美女人！<span lang=\"EN-US\">..<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27.05pt;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent2;mso-themetint:153\">美颜天敌：黄褐斑</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;mso-themecolor:accent2;\r\nmso-themetint:153\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;mso-themecolor:accent2;\r\nmso-themetint:153\">黄褐斑也称为蝴蝶斑或肝斑斑，是发生在面部的色给沉着斑。黄褐斑常见于女性脸部，好发于两颊、额、鼻、上唇等部位，呈黄褐色或深褐色斑片，大小不等，形状不规则，无自觉症状，夏季容易加深。内分泌失调，长期口服避孕药、营养不良、贫血，长期便秘、痛经、慢性盆腔炎、妇科疾病、不明原因的慢性疾病、以及日光照射等都是黄褐斑的发生原因。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;mso-themecolor:accent2;\r\nmso-themetint:153\">美容天敌：便秘</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;mso-themecolor:accent2;mso-themetint:153\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;mso-themecolor:accent2;\r\nmso-themetint:153\">便秘容易增加人体体内毒素，使机体新陈代谢紊乱、内颁发推敲及微量元素不均衡，从而导致皮肤暗淡无光、、面色无华、毛发枯干、并产生、黄褐斑、痤疮、口臭等。长期便秘不仅会使面色晦暗、精神不振、小腹凸出，还容易引发乳腺癌、高血压等多种疾病。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;mso-themecolor:accent2;\r\nmso-themetint:153\">美丽源于<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>内<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>身体内在健康了，肌肤自然会散发着迷人的光泽，脸色也会水嫩红润，这是单纯依靠化妆品无法达到的境界。其实在生活中，有不少中药成分具有养颜排毒的功效，让女人由内而外，赢得健康和美丽。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;mso-themecolor:accent2;\r\nmso-themetint:153\">丹参阿胶珍珠胶囊是集众家之所长，集古今之精典，集食药为一炉，从食养再生、调养气血入手来调节人体内部的阴阳平衡，进行养颜美容的。通过有效调节体内各项机能，生清降浊，推动血脉和津液运行，内活气血，<span lang=\"EN-US\">**</span>疾病，外祛色斑，美白肌肤；对女性皮肤暗疮和美白也有很好的效果；对失眠<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span>痛经月经不调<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span>头疼效果明显。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;mso-themecolor:accent2;\r\nmso-themetint:153\">阿胶</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;mso-themecolor:accent2;mso-themetint:153\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;mso-themecolor:accent2;\r\nmso-themetint:153\">中医认为，阿胶具有补血止血、滋阴润燥、美容养颜、润经安胎等作用，可改善血虚萎黄、眩晕、肌痿无力，肺燥咳嗽、吐血尿血、便血崩漏等现象。现代医学研究表明，阿胶提取物能促进红细胞和血红蛋白的生成，有明显的补血作用，不但可以改善贫血，还有、耐缺氧、耐寒冷、健脑、延缓衰老和促进淋巴细胞转化的作用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;mso-themecolor:accent2;\r\nmso-themetint:153\">珍珠</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;mso-themecolor:accent2;mso-themetint:153\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;mso-themecolor:accent2;\r\nmso-themetint:153\">珍珠自古就是美容养颜的名贵中药材，中医认为珍珠有安神定惊，清扫解毒，收敛生肌、明目消翳、白嫩肌肤之功效。现代医学研究表明、珍珠中含有<span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span>多种氨基酸，有助于皮肤细胞的新陈代谢及对营养成分的吸收，具有美容增白、祛斑、延缓衰老的作用，此外还能调节免疫力、改善记忆力和提高视力。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;mso-themecolor:accent2;\r\nmso-themetint:153\">乌（骨）鸡</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;mso-themecolor:accent2;mso-themetint:153\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;mso-themecolor:accent2;\r\nmso-themetint:153\">中医认为，乌（骨）鸡有补肝益肾、益气养血、养阴退热之功效。现代医学研究表明，乌（骨）鸡中含有<span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span>种氨基酸、其中丝氨酸、苏氨酸可预防皮肤老化、酪氨酸具有吸收日光中紫外线功能、对保护皮肤、消除斑痕、细腻肌肤有特殊作用。此外，乌（骨）鸡中的铁、锌、镁、锶、钼含量较高，维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">E</span>含量比普通鸡肉高<span lang=\"EN-US\">2~6</span>倍，因此具有增强免疫力，延缓衰老、抗疲劳的作用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;mso-themecolor:accent2;\r\nmso-themetint:153\">丹参</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;mso-themecolor:accent2;mso-themetint:153\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;mso-themecolor:accent2;\r\nmso-themetint:153\">丹参也叫血参、红参或此紫丹参，为唇形科多年生草本，药用根茎。中医认为，丹参有活血化瘀、调经止痕、养血安神、清心除烦之功效。现代医学研究表明，丹参提取物有<span lang=\"EN-US\">SOD</span>（超氧化岐化酶）相似的抗氧化作用，对保护心脑血管和肝脏、改善睡眠、抗肿瘤有良好的保健作用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;mso-themecolor:accent2;\r\nmso-themetint:153\">当归</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;mso-themecolor:accent2;mso-themetint:153\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;mso-themecolor:accent2;\r\nmso-themetint:153\">当归味甘、辛、性温，具有补血、活血、调经、润燥、滑肠之功效，可帮助改善月经不调、贫血、痛经、崩漏、血虚、便秘等现象。现代医学研究表明，当归提取物有改善贫血、保护肝脏、抗血栓、降血压、增强免疫力、抗炎抑菌、抗肿瘤等作用。此外，当归提取物还能抑制黑色素生成，扩张皮肤毛细血管，使皮肤滋润光泽、弹性增加，有助于改善黄褐斑等色素性皮肤病。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;mso-themecolor:accent2;\r\nmso-themetint:153\">薏仁</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;mso-themecolor:accent2;mso-themetint:153\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;mso-themecolor:accent2;\r\nmso-themetint:153\">薏仁性凉、味甘、淡、入脾、肾经、具有利水、健脾、清热排脓的功效，且有关容作用。中医认为，薏仁有健脾利湿、清热排脓功能，可改善脾虚泄泻、水肿脚气、关节疼痛等现象。现代医学研究表明，薏仁具有一定的抑菌、抗病毒功能、长期食用、可以增强免疫力、降血糖、抑制肿瘤、改善睡眠，还能使皮肤光滑细腻、白净有光泽。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#D99594;mso-themecolor:accent2;\r\nmso-themetint:153\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#D99594;mso-themecolor:accent2;mso-themetint:153\"><img src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/697639576/T2iKraXlVXXXXXXXXX_!!697639576.jpg\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#D99594;mso-themecolor:accent2;mso-themetint:153\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:22.0pt;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">疑难解答<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 45.05pt; text-indent: -18pt;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">1.<span style=\"font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">丹参阿胶珍珠胶囊是淡化色斑还是彻底清除色斑？</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">色斑的形成不是一天两天而为，如果短期内彻底清除不易<span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span>丹参阿胶珍珠胶囊主要是淡化色斑，服用时间越长，淡化效果越好，直到彻底清除色斑。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:45.05pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">2.<span style=\"font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">祛斑产品有可能暂时淡化，会不会不使用以后又会反复？</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">祛斑产品丹参阿胶珍珠胶囊属天然物种提取，可以随时停服，停服以后不会反复，注意多休息、维护良好的生活习惯，就不会让消除的斑斑重现回到脸上。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:45.05pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">3.<span style=\"font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">我是遗传性雀斑、色斑，丹参阿胶珍珠胶囊对我能有效吗？</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">色斑、雀斑的形成很少是受遗传所为，大多数都是因为生活习惯相同导致家庭成员都有雀斑、色斑，男士皮肤较女士而言，敏感性较弱，所以不易产生色斑、痘痘，因此任何斑斑都可以服用本品淡化直到消除。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:45.05pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">4.<span style=\"font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">丹参阿胶珍珠胶囊主要祛除何种斑？</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">祛斑产品丹参阿胶珍珠胶囊本品主要以调理为主，针对色斑、雀斑、黄褐斑等都有不同程度的效果。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:黑体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<div class=\"marginleft\" style=\"margin-left: 14px; font-family: Simsun;\">\r\n<div id=\"txt_ulli\" style=\"width: 706px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span id=\"Label_Content\"> </span></div>\r\n</div>', 'images/201306/thumb_img/205_thumb_G_1370064848782.gif', 'images/201306/goods_img/205_