t; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">月，完美芦荟牙膏被中华预防医学会列入健康金桥重点工程。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:45.0pt;text-indent:27.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\"><img src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/1032624139/T21wHHXfVaXXXXXXXX_!!1032624139.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/1032624139/T2P_SsXdFcXXXXXXXX_!!1032624139.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/1032624139/T21lbvXXlbXXXXXXXX_!!1032624139.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:45.0pt;text-indent:27.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:45.0pt;text-indent:48.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 24pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 黑体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">完美芦荟牙膏实验说明<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:45.0pt;text-indent:48.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 24pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:45.0pt;text-indent:27.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">一、接种：将已经繁殖生长旺盛的细菌接种在新牙刷上，而后进行恒温、恒湿培养。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:45.0pt;text-indent:27.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">二、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">10</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">天后，我们看到牙刷上生长了许多细菌，接种成功。这时我们将三种不同品牌的牙膏挤在这样的牙刷上，其中</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">P</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">是完美芦荟牙膏，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">CL</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">CP</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">是市场上高档品牌的其它两种牙膏，同时保留一支牙刷上不涂牙膏做为空白试验，这样我们将它们继续进行恒温、恒湿培养。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:45.0pt;text-indent:27.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">三、第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">20</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">天：经过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">10</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">天的培养，空白牙刷上已经长满了细菌，而完美牙膏已将细菌杀死，其它两个品牌的牙膏对这些细菌几乎没有任何抑制作用，尤其是这支</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">CL</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">白色的牙膏不但不能杀死细菌，反而使这些细菌生长得更加茁壮。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:45.0pt;text-indent:27.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">四、第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">30</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">天：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">30</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">天过去了，没涂牙膏的牙刷长满了细菌，完美牙膏不断渗透到牙刷的底部已将牙刷上的细菌杀灭，而其它两个品牌</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">CL</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">CP</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">的牙膏几乎与没有涂牙膏的牙刷一样长满了细菌，这证明它们对细菌没有任何抑制作用，通过这组试验，证明了在同样的条件下即使是市场上高档品牌牙膏对口腔中有害的细菌也往往无能为力，而完美芦荟牙膏却有很强的抑菌作用，在面对选用理想的牙膏，保持口腔清洁、牙齿健康的首要问题时，只有完美芦荟牙膏才是我们放心的选择。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:45.0pt;text-indent:27.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">口腔健康，从最佳选择开始，完美芦荟牙膏套装，满足您的口腔自然生理规律，让您笑得自然，口气清新，充满自信，伴你度过健康浪漫每一天！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:20.9pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:.87;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 24pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 黑体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:20.9pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:.87;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 24pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 黑体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:20.9pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:.87;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 24pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 黑体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:20.9pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:.87;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 24pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 黑体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:20.9pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:.87;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 24pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 黑体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">产品问答</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 24pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">、问：完美芦荟牙膏有何成份特点？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">答：有完美三合一配方，包括天然芦荟、玉洁纯及双氟。与众不同的是，它采用二氧化硅作为磨擦剂，即使是最稚嫩的乳牙也不会磨损，并且口感非常好，除了薄荷香味，还有完美香型，而且膏体透明晶莹、质地优良。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">、问：为什么完美芦荟牙膏对牙周炎有效果？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">答：因为完美芦荟牙膏含有广谱高效杀菌剂玉洁纯，能有效杀灭口腔中有害微生物。同时所含芦荟成份，亦有消炎杀菌、促进伤口愈口功能。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">、问：完美芦荟牙膏为什么能防龋齿？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">答：完美芦荟牙膏中特别添加的双氟<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>氟化钠、单氟磷酸钠<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>。可将牙釉质中耐酸的羟磷灰石转变为耐酸又耐磨的氟磷灰石，从而达到了防龋齿效果。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">、问：双氟是什么，有什么作用？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">答：双氟是指氟化钠和单氟磷酸钠。双氟相线补充，提供活性氟，使牙齿能够耐酸性、防腐蚀，而且可再生珐琅质，以补充因每天咀嚼食物而磨损的牙齿。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">5</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">、问：玉洁纯是什么物质？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">答：是目前世界上最先进抗菌消炎剂，具有广谱高效、无刺激性、去肿消炎作用尤为显著，能彻底消除口腔残留物和微生物。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">6</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">、什么是玉洁纯<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP</span>？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">答：玉洁纯<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP</span>是经过严格的高技术分离，将玉洁新<span lang=\"EN-US\">DP300</span>中一种广谱的极低量的某些不纯物降至最低水平，从而最大限度地保证了口腔卫生用品在使用中对人体的安全性。玉洁纯<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP</span>是专用于口腔卫生用品的原料，具有以下突出优点：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">①广谱抗菌性，除可抑杀包括细菌和真菌在内的多种菌外，对于口腔中的致病菌有独特的抑杀效果，玉洁纯不仅对千万牙龈炎、牙周炎的致病菌有高效的抑杀作用，还有助于去除牙菌斑，预防牙龈炎、龋齿等；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">②使用后具有持久抗菌效果，能够长时间附着在牙齿或口腔表面，形成保护膜，温柔呵护您的口腔；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">③对口腔及口腔粘膜无刺激及过敏反应；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">④口感良好，不经肝肾代谢，直接排出体外，对人体安全；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">⑤用于含氟牙膏中，可与氟化物发生协调增效作用，既能强力抑杀病菌，又能促进氟化物对牙釉质的再生修复作用，增强牙齿牢固性，使之能承受长时间的咀嚼和摩擦压力；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">⑥经欧美及各大跨国公司几十年来的广泛长期使用，证明玉洁纯对人类及环境非常安全。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:45.0pt;text-indent:27.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">正是基于以上结论，近年来被广泛用于牙膏、漱口水、口香剂等口腔卫生用品中，并畅销世界各地，从综合效果来看，玉洁纯<span lang=\"EN-US\">MP</span>是当今世界首屈一指的抗菌剂。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:45.0pt;text-indent:27.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:黑体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<div class=\"marginleft\" style=\"margin-left: 14px; font-family: Simsun;\">\r\n<div id=\"txt_ulli\" style=\"width: 706px; 