order: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px;\"><img src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/420635408/T2Zqj6XbhXXXXXXXXX_!!420635408.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none;\" /><img src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/420635408/T2qqz6Xa4XXXXXXXXX_!!420635408.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none;\" /><img src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/420635408/T2O090Xk8bXXXXXXXX_!!420635408.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none;\" /><img src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/420635408/T2r2_5XotXXXXXXXXX_!!420635408.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none;\" /><img src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/420635408/T2T4P4XndXXXXXXXXX_!!420635408.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none;\" /><img src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/420635408/T2Mh65XoFXXXXXXXXX_!!420635408.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none;\" /><img src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/420635408/T229JsXjpMXXXXXXXX_!!420635408.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none;\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 22pt; line-height: 43px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">换换口气<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>有好运气</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 22pt; line-height: 43px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">有这样一个<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>四有新人<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>，他有大学毕业文凭，有较强的语言表达能力，有较好的外部形象和内在气质，还有对待生活的一颗火热的心。然而，就是这样一个优秀的年轻人，在现实中却运气不佳，屡屡受挫。用他自己的话来形容，就是一无所有。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">一次相亲时，他和女孩都产生了相互倾慕之意，朋友也认为他们是天造地设的一对。然而，接触过几次之后，女孩<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>紧急刹车<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>，没有作出任何解释，年轻人出乎意料。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">一次应聘时，他本人非常希望有机会在那家公司发展，招聘代表对他的个人资料也非常感兴趣。然而就在面试后，对方却突然委婉地拒绝了他，年轻人莫名其妙。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">后来，他终于找到一份推销员的工作。产品的销路十分看好，然而，他却业绩平平，甚至比那些综合能力较弱的同事还差一大截。他自己也发现，有些顾客根本不愿同他多作交谈，年轻人百思不得其解。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">一系列的打击之后：年轻人开始埋怨命运的不济，老天爷的不公，甚至有些自暴自弃。直到有一天，年轻人一个最好的朋友坦诚地指出了他的<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>克星<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>所在，并赠送给他一个</span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); font-weight: normal;\">&ldquo;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); font-weight: normal;\">秘密武器<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">，年轻人的命运从此发生了重大转折。不久，一个美丽动人的女孩爱上了他；一家前景广阔的大公司录用了他；业务活动中同行及顾客都非常喜欢与他打交道。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">其实，对付年轻人爱情及事业上<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>克星<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>的<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>秘密武器<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>，不是别的，</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); font-weight: normal;\">就是一支完美芦荟喷雾口香剂</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">。口气一变，好运就来。改变命运也许就是这么简单！<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27.05pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: red;\">相关知识链接</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: red;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27.05pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">口腔异味测试三种方法：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">①</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">将手掌竖立靠近在嘴前，深呼吸后呵出一口气，同时用鼻子迅速闻嗅；<span lang=\"EN-US\">②</span>用洗净的手指从舌头和牙齿分别沾一些唾液，放在鼻子下边搓边闻；<span lang=\"EN-US\">③</span>与朋友近距离对话时，询问对方的感受。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27.05pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">口控异味形成的三种原因：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">①</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">食用某些食物会在口腔产生较长时间保留刺激性气味，如葱、蒜、羊肉等；<span lang=\"EN-US\">②</span>某些牙龈疾病及牙缝食物残渣会产生腐臭气味；<span lang=\"EN-US\">③</span>某些内脏器质性病变会产生相应的异味，如消化系统疾病等。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 22pt; line-height: 43px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">完美芦荟喷雾口香剂</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 22pt; line-height: 43px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">完美芦荟喷雾口香剂含有多种独特配方，其中芦荟、春黄菊提取物、玉洁纯、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">E</span>的功效尤为显著。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27.05pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">主要成分：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">①</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">含有浓缩</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">芦荟精华<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">能帮助消炎和促进组织再生，加速伤口愈合，</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">治愈口腔溃疡</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">；<span lang=\"EN-US\">②</span></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">春黄菊提取物<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">生长在欧洲，有良好的</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">消炎、止痛、消肿、促进细胞再生，加速溃疡愈合</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">的作用，在欧洲被广泛用于口腔护理；<span lang=\"EN-US\">③</span></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">玉洁纯<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">一种国际流行的新型高效广谱抗菌剂，它可以消除口腔中的有害细菌，保持口腔环境健康、干净；<span lang=\"EN-US\">④</span></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">E--</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">具有软化、滋润皮肤，防衰老等作用，使我们永保青春。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">平时我们吃的东西如葱、蒜等或者口腔有异味的，我们去异味的办法大多是嚼口香糖，其实这个习惯给我们的健康带来了危害。经科学家研究发现口香糖中含有<span lang=\"EN-US\">DPOD</span>和<span lang=\"EN-US\">BPOG</span>两种增塑剂，都是</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">有毒的物质</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">，每天嚼<span lang=\"EN-US\">7--8</span>块</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">口香糖</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">，便会达到人体中毒的剂量，</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">影响食欲</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">，危及健康。而且口香糖中含有大量的糖份，容易使口腔细菌滋生并活跃，引起</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">蛀牙</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">等口腔疾病，长期咀嚼将引起口腔异味加重。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">另外嚼口香糖有时会影响我们的形象，特别是在一些公众场合不雅观，而且口香糖的胶状物吐到地上，影响环境卫生，给我们的生活带来诸多不便。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27.05pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">产品功效和特点：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">①</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">生津解渴、提神醒脑</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">；<span lang=\"EN-US\">②</span></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-he