:#00B050;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;\r\nmso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">将喷头对准口腔轻按喷入，每瓶至少可使用<span lang=\"EN-US\">240</span>次。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/420635408/T2Zqj6XbhXXXXXXXXX_!!420635408.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/420635408/T2qqz6Xa4XXXXXXXXX_!!420635408.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/420635408/T2O090Xk8bXXXXXXXX_!!420635408.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/420635408/T2r2_5XotXXXXXXXXX_!!420635408.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/420635408/T2T4P4XndXXXXXXXXX_!!420635408.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/420635408/T2Mh65XoFXXXXXXXXX_!!420635408.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/420635408/T229JsXjpMXXXXXXXX_!!420635408.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:22.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050\">换换口气<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>有好运气</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:22.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">有这样一个<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>四有新人<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>，他有大学毕业文凭，有较强的语言表达能力，有较好的外部形象和内在气质，还有对待生活的一颗火热的心。然而，就是这样一个优秀的年轻人，在现实中却运气不佳，屡屡受挫。用他自己的话来形容，就是一无所有。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">一次相亲时，他和女孩都产生了相互倾慕之意，朋友也认为他们是天造地设的一对。然而，接触过几次之后，女孩<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>紧急刹车<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>，没有作出任何解释，年轻人出乎意料。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">一次应聘时，他本人非常希望有机会在那家公司发展，招聘代表对他的个人资料也非常感兴趣。然而就在面试后，对方却突然委婉地拒绝了他，年轻人莫名其妙。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">后来，他终于找到一份推销员的工作。产品的销路十分看好，然而，他却业绩平平，甚至比那些综合能力较弱的同事还差一大截。他自己也发现，有些顾客根本不愿同他多作交谈，年轻人百思不得其解。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">一系列的打击之后：年轻人开始埋怨命运的不济，老天爷的不公，甚至有些自暴自弃。直到有一天，年轻人一个最好的朋友坦诚地指出了他的<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>克星<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>所在，并赠送给他一个</span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">&ldquo;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">秘密武器<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">，年轻人的命运从此发生了重大转折。不久，一个美丽动人的女孩爱上了他；一家前景广阔的大公司录用了他；业务活动中同行及顾客都非常喜欢与他打交道。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">其实，对付年轻人爱情及事业上<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>克星<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>的<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>秘密武器<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>，不是别的，</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">就是一支完美芦荟喷雾口香剂</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">。口气一变，好运就来。改变命运也许就是这么简单！<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:red\">相关知识链接</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:red\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050\">口腔异味测试三种方法：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050\">①</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">将手掌竖立靠近在嘴前，深呼吸后呵出一口气，同时用鼻子迅速闻嗅；<span lang=\"EN-US\">②</span>用洗净的手指从舌头和牙齿分别沾一些唾液，放在鼻子下边搓边闻；<span lang=\"EN-US\">③</span>与朋友近距离对话时，询问对方的感受。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050\">口控异味形成的三种原因：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050\">①</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">食用某些食物会在口腔产生较长时间保留刺激性气味，如葱、蒜、羊肉等；<span lang=\"EN-US\">②</span>某些牙龈疾病及牙缝食物残渣会产生腐臭气味；<span lang=\"EN-US\">③</span>某些内脏器质性病变会产生相应的异味，如消化系统疾病等。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:22.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050\">完美芦荟喷雾口香剂</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:22.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">完美芦荟喷雾口香剂含有多种独特配方，其中芦荟、春黄菊提取物、玉洁纯、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">E</span>的功效尤为显著。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050\">主要成分：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050\">①</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">含有浓缩</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050\">芦荟精华<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">能帮助消炎和促进组织再生，加速伤口愈合，</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050\">治愈口腔溃疡</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">；<span lang=\"EN-US\">②</span></span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050\">春黄菊提取物<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">生长在欧洲，有良好的</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050\">消炎、止痛、消肿、促进细胞再生，加速溃疡愈合</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">的作用，在欧洲被广泛用于口腔护理；<span lang=\"EN-US\">③</span></span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050\">玉洁纯<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">一种国际流行的新型高效广谱抗菌剂，它可以消除口腔中的有害细菌，保持口腔环境健康、干净；<span lang=\"EN-US\">④</span></span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050\">维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">E--</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">具有软化、滋润皮肤，防衰老等作用，使我们永保青春。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">平时我们吃的东西如葱、蒜等或者口腔有异味的，我们去异味的办法大多是嚼口香糖，其实这个习惯给我们的健康带来了危害。经科学家研究发现口香糖中含有<span lang=\"EN-US\">DPOD</span>和<span lang=\"EN-US\">BPOG</span>两种增塑剂，都是</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050\">有毒的物质</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">，每天嚼<span lang=\"EN-US\">7--8</span>块</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050\">口香糖</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">，便会达到人体中毒的剂量，</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050\">影响食欲</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">，危及健康。而且口香糖中含有大量的糖份，容易使口腔细菌滋生并活跃，引起</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050\">蛀牙</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">等口腔疾病，长期咀嚼将引起口腔异味加重。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">另外嚼口香糖有时会影响我们的形象，特别是在一些公众场合不雅观，而且口香糖的胶状物吐到地上，影响环境卫生，给我们的生活带来诸多不便。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050\">产品功效和特点：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050\">①</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050\">生津解渴、提神醒脑</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">；<span lang=\"EN-US\">②</span></span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050\">缓解口腔溃疡、牙龈肿痛、咳嗽和咽喉炎症</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">，完美芦荟口香剂所含的成份能迅速缓解以上症状；<span lang=\"EN-US\">③</span>减少肺部疾病；<span lang=\"EN-US\">④</span>能起到花露水、清凉油和风精油的作用，在疲惫、犯困或精力不集中时，</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050\">揉擦到太阳穴或鼻翼处</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">，能使您精神焕发、神清气爽；<span lang=\"EN-US\">⑤</span>消除口臭和口腔异味，使口气更加清新。增进人际关系，拉近人与人之间距离，为您带来成功机缘；<span lang=\"EN-US\">⑥</span>无糖配置，不会损坏牙齿；<span lang=\"EN-US\">⑦</span></span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050\">不含酒精</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">成份，不会刺激口腔粘膜；<span lang=\"EN-US\">⑧</span>采用喷压式雾状，喷附面积大，喷后口腔内存留淡淡的清凉味道，使您的谈吐更有自信。长期使用，有利于口腔健康；<span lang=\"EN-US\">⑨</span></span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050\">携带方便</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050\">--</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">体积较小，高度仅为<span lang=\"EN-US\">8cm</span>，直径仅为<span lang=\"EN-US\">2cm</span>（与一支唇膏差不多大），置于衣服口袋、手袋均可；<span lang=\"EN-US\">⑩</span>每支<span lang=\"EN-US\">15ml</span>，可喷<span lang=\"EN-US\">240</span>次以上，每次不到<span lang=\"EN-US\">0.1</span>元，而口香糖每次<span lang=\"EN-US\">0.3</span>元。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:黑体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<div class=\"marginleft\" style=\"margin-left: 14px; font-family: Simsun;\">\r\n<div id=\"txt_ulli\" style=\"width: 706px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span id=\"Label_Content\"> </span></div>\r\n</div>', 'images/201306/thumb_img/208_thumb_G_1370057972605