n><strong><span style=\"font-size: 24pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(51, 51, 255); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">完美荟新去头屑洗发露</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(51, 51, 255); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><em><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(51, 51, 255); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">成分及功能：</span></b></em><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#3333FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(51, 51, 255); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">在我们日常生活中，很多人因头皮屑而烦恼，有人误认为头发没有洗干净，于是经常洗发，但干了以后头皮屑又出来了，其实头皮屑是真菌感染引起的，最有效的去屑方法是杀灭真菌。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(51, 51, 255); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">荟新去头屑洗发露内含<span lang=\"EN-US\">ZPT</span>。<span lang=\"EN-US\">ZPT</span>的学名叫去头屑活性因子，它是能有效防止糠秕孢子菌的抗真菌剂，<strong><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">对引起头皮屑的真菌有较强的杀灭作用，能彻底去除头皮屑</span></strong>，它还含有天然去屑止痒剂芦荟，芦荟能起到双重调理，有效去除头皮屑和止痒，令秀发洁净、飘洒自如、魅力无穷。荟新去头屑洗发露含有头皮平衡因子调理剂：它能调理皮脂腺分泌的油脂；防静电剂：它使头发易梳理，不起静电<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(51, 51, 255); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">荟新去头屑洗发露具有<strong><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">改善头部皮肤的养护能力</span></strong>，其滋润及护发成份能充分补给头发营养素，锁住头发水份，令秀发时刻柔顺易梳，荟新去头屑洗发露采用温和配方，<strong><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">去头屑不伤秀发</span></strong>，功效独特，经常使用，能<strong><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">有效防止头屑再次出现</span></strong>，呵护头发健康生长。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(51, 51, 255); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">全新滋养去屑配方，轻松去除头屑，并滋润头发，帮助您摆脱头屑的烦恼！含活性<span lang=\"EN-US\">ZPT</span>和水扬酸酯，双重作用，有效去屑止痒；温和配方，清洁头发而不伤发；<span lang=\"EN-US\">Biomin Acquacinque</span>，含多种微量元素及营养成分，促进细胞新陈代谢，使头发更有弹性；芦荟、野菊花提取物，有效修复头发表皮鳞片的损伤，锁住头发水分，使头发自然亮泽，乌黑动人；适用于各种发质；与荟新保湿修护型润发乳配合使用，效果更佳。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(51, 51, 255); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">使用方法：</span></em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(51, 51, 255); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">先将头发淋湿，再倒取适量荟新去头屑洗发露，揉洗头发至泡沫最多最细，使<span lang=\"EN-US\">ZPT</span>充分发挥去除头皮屑作用之后，再用清水冲净即可。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(51, 51, 255); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">小贴士：头屑是怎样产生的？</span></em><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#3333FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(51, 51, 255); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">真正的头屑其实和一种名为糠孢子菌的微生物有关，糠秕孢子菌的数量如超出正常水平，头屑就产生了。荟新去头屑洗发露里面的<span lang=\"EN-US\">ZPT</span>主要目的不是杀死正常菌落中所有的现存微生物，而是把糠秕孢子菌的数量减少至正常水平，从而有效抑制和去除头屑。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:22.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:黑体;color:#3333FF\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:22.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:黑体;color:#3333FF\">产品问答</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:22.0pt;line-height:150%;color:#3333FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#3333FF\">1、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;