\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#CC00FF;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">离子表面活性剂</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">。均匀、牢固地依附在发干上，而使发干表面光滑平整，因而使用后使头发显得光亮、柔软如丝，且富有弹性。其中所含的</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#CC00FF;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">抗静电添加剂</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">能防止头发上聚集电荷而相互缠绕，使头发开叉的主要原因之一就是由于</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#CC00FF;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">发梳对头发的过度摩擦</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">。使用护发素一方面能使发干表面光滑平整，另一方面又可避免头发因静电而相互缠绕，所以在很大程度上减轻发梳与头发的摩擦而避免头发开叉。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">荟新保湿修护型润发乳含天然芦荟、氨基酸、维生素</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">B5</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">和维生素</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;color:#CC00FF\">E</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">及天然保湿成份，它能深入发根滋养头发，形成保护膜，使头发恢复生机，令枯黄、干燥、分叉等敏感、脆弱、受损伤的头发重现光彩，长期使用，能有效保持头发纤维细胞的含水量，且对紫外线及吹风、烫发、染发，特别是受损、敏感型头发，使用一段时间后，头发像皮筋一样有弹性，坚持使用荟新营养洗发露和荟新保湿修护型润发乳，一定会让您的秀发更加飘逸、展现亮丽风彩</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">!<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">全新的保湿滋润配方，加入多种天然植物成分，使头发更健康、坚韧。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">蕴含天然植物角蛋白，有效修护染烫等受损头发；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">HYDROVITON </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">保湿因子及天然乳木果油，</span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">24 </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#CC00FF;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">小时长效保湿</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">，使秀发更柔顺；</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#CC00FF;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">天然海藻糖</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">，在头发上形成一层保护膜，防止头发表层水分流失；维他命</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">E</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">、维他命原</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;color:#CC00FF\">B5</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">，补充头发营养，由发根至发梢全面滋养秀发；芦荟、灵芝以及蜂蜜提取物，深入发芯，营养修复受损头发，令秀发健康有弹性、亮泽；独特的香薰配方，香味清新怡人，令您每天都有愉快的心情；适用于各种发质。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;楷体_GB2312&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#CC00FF\">使用方法：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">使用荟新系列洗发露洗净头发，再倒取适量荟新保湿修护型润发乳，轻揉头发约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">分钟，待头发充分吸收养份后，再用清水冲净即可。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:#CC00FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">让秀发如丝般顺滑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-fareast-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">&mdash;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:黑体;color:#CC00FF\">完美荟新三宝（营养洗发露、去头屑洗发露、保湿修护型润发乳）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">为什么洗发和护发要分开？我们先来了解一下头发的结构：头发由里到外可分三层</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">--</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">里面是髓质层；中间是皮质层；外面是角质层。角质层是由</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">6--12</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">层鳞片组成。油脂、污垢、灰尘等物质都藏在这些鳞片中。洗发水的作用就是打开鳞片，清洗里面的脏物。而护发素的作用是给足头发营养后关闭鳞片。这就象开门、关门不能同时进行一样，洗发、护发也要分开进行。市面上的产品为了迎合市场需要，采用二合一、三合一的洗护用品，在这些产品中加入了硅酮这种物质。硅酮是皮革亮洁剂的主要成分，长时间使用会使头发无光泽、枯黄、易断裂、对头发的损害非常大。完美公司的洗护用品，一直都是洗护分开，适合各类发质的消费群。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:22.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:黑体;color:#CC00FF\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:22.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:黑体;color:#CC00FF\">产品问答</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:22.0pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">1、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">问：为什么称为荟新系列</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">?<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">答：很简单，三个新产品都含芦荟成份，也有新配方，所以统称为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">荟新系列</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;color:#CC00FF\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">2、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">问：正确的洗头方法是什么</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">?<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">答：用温水，用我们的指腹轻轻按摩的方式来进行洗发。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">3、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">问：我们的护发素有什么特别的地方</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">?<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">答：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">①</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">含胶原蛋白及维生素</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">B5</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">，迅速渗透到发囊；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">②</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">含头发柔软剂，令头发柔软，光滑如丝；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">③</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">含有特别的秘方使所有的营养成份被吸收。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">4、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">问：荟新去头屑洗发露里面的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">ZPT</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">真正名称叫什么</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">?</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">有何作用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">?<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">答：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">ZPI</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">的学名叫去头屑活性因子，它是能有效防止糠秕孢子菌的抗真菌剂，而且对头部皮肤绝无损伤。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">5、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">问：头屑是怎样产生的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">?&nbsp;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">答：真正的头屑其实和一种名为糠孢子菌的微生物有关，糠秕袍子菌的数量如超出正常水平，头屑就产生了。荟新去头屑洗发露里面的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">ZPT</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">主要目的不是杀死正常菌落中所有的现存微生物，而是把糠秕孢子菌的数量减少至正常水平，从而有效抑制和去除头屑。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">6、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">问：天天洗发会导致头皮屑增多吗</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">? <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">答：这是表面假象，真正的罪魁祸首其实是不正确的洗发方式。正确的洗发方法应该是用指腹轻轻按摩头皮，并且要选择好造合自己发质的洗发水，配合适中水温</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">25</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n宋体;color:#CC00FF\">℃</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;color:#CC00FF\">--45</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#CC00FF\">℃</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">是适宜的温度。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">7、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">问、为什么荟新营养洗发露、荟新去头屑洗发露要分开使用？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">答：头发的表层是鳞状角质层，荟新营养洗发露的主要功能是清除角质层中灰尘，而荟新去头屑洗发露的主要功能是护理、柔顺发质，若两者合一会影响护发效果。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">8、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">问：荟新营养洗发露适合于哪种发质</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">?<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">答：因为它内含芦荟、氨基酸、羊胎素等特效修补成份，所以荟新营养洗发露适用于各种发质。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">9、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">问：荟新营养洗发露有护发作用吗？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">答：有。因为它含有芦荟、氨基酸、羊胎素等护发成份；在洗发的同时给予头发充分的护理。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">10、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">问：荟新营养洗发露适合油性发质的人吗</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">?<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">答：适合。因为它是一个综合性的护理洗发露，适用于各种发质。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">11、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">问：荟新营养洗发露可以去头屑吗</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">?<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">答：不可以。如果有头屑的话最好选用我们的荟新去头屑洗发露。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">12、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">问：荟新去头屑洗发露有护发润发功效吗</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">?<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">答：有。因为产品中含有滋润及护发成份，能充分补给头发营养素。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">13、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">问：没有头皮屑的人可以使用荟新去头屑洗发露吗</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">?<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">答：可以。并且适合于各种发质的人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">14、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">问：用荟新去头屑洗发露洗头会不会掉头发</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">?<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">答：不会。因为它含有特效头皮平衡因子，并且采用温和配方，去头屑的同时不伤发，也不会掉头发。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">15、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">问：荟新修护型护发素可以拿来洗头发吗</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">?<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">答：不可以。因为它只是一种修护型的护发素，没有清洁作用，只有修护头发的作用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\"><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 16</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">、问：护发素可以拿来当摩丝用吗</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">?<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">答：可以。但是我们不提倡这样用，因为这样不卫生。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">17、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">问：护发素可不可以拿来当油膏用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">?<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">答：不需要。只要我们在日常洗头时配合荟新修护型护发素来用，就可以达到油膏的效果。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">18、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">问：荟新系列洗发露浓度不足，稀似水，感觉不好</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">?<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">答：荟新系列洗发露是根据市场调查，为适应广大消费者的习惯而研制其粘度的，所以荟新系列洗发露的粘度是更适合大多数消费者的，其中的有效物质使其洗护的作用更好，一种优质的产品是不宜用稀稠来判断的。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">19</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">、问：做试验时</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">用矿泉水的瓶子加少许水摇两下</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">发现去头屑洗发露与营养洗发露效果不同，去头屑洗发露是浊水。护理洗发露是清明透亮的，为什么</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">?<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">答：两种洗发露属于不同体系，营养型属于表面活性剂体系，去头屑属于乳化体系，添加有不溶于水的头发调理剂，故会不透亮，但都是很好的洗发露。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">19、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">问：用荟新去头屑洗发露洗头，有脱头发的现象。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">答：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">①</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">有头皮屑时，才使用荟新去头屑洗发露，如果没有头皮屑，请用荟新营养洗发露；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">②</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">对于头发根部卵状糠疹癣菌较多的客户，由于荟新去头屑因子</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">ZPT</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">杀菌力较强，洗头时若用力过大，可能会有脱发现象，故洗发用力要适中；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">③</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">饮食、睡眠、精神状态方面欠佳及气候的原因有时也会导致大量头皮屑产生，进而导致易脱发；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">④</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">使用去头屑洗发露，一定要冲洗干净；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">⑤</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">当开始使用一种新晶牌的洗发水时，头皮组织会有一个适应的阶段，此时期内也可能会脱发。坚持使用一段时间后，则会好转。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">20、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#CC00FF\">问：完美芦荟护发素能和洗发水同时使用吗</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\">?<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#CC00FF\">答：不能。正确的方法是：先洗发，后护发。可达到理想的洗发、护发效果。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#CC00FF\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', 'images/201305/thumb_img/212_thumb_G_1369801186622.png', 'images/201305/goods_img/212_G_1369801186106.jpg', 'images/201305/source_img/212_G_1369801186569.png', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1369456004', '71', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1371143056', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '');
