文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">、温和润肤乳具有清洁肌肤，去除死皮，洗去多余油脂的功效。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">4</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">、芦荟提取物，太阳花油能营养、滋润皮肤，并与润肤乳在皮肤表面形成保护膜，使肌肤如丝般幼滑娇嫩。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">5</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">、蕴含超浓缩芦荟精华，将面部护理技术运用至全身，细心清洁，呵护您身体的每一寸肌肤。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">6</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">、散发自然清香，唤醒您神采飞扬的美丽气质。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">7</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">、长期使用，可帮助改善肌肤暗哑，令肌肤莹润有光泽。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">◆：适用于干性</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">/</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">中性</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">/</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">敏感性</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">/</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">极干性肌肤及干燥气候使用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">◆：夏天使用不油腻，冬天使用不干燥。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">产品用法：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">先将皮肤润湿，取适量完美芦荟沐浴露涂于湿润过的皮肤上，用手或沐浴球</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">/</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">海绵轻揉皮肤至泡沫最丰富时，再用清水洗净即可，如重复上述动作（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">DOUBLE ACTION</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">）可达更佳效果。<b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">注意：应存放在通风阴凉处，避免日晒。如不慎入眼，请立即用清水洗净。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><img src=\"http://img.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/84155695/T2czZaXa8XXXXXXXXX_!!84155695.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none;\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27.05pt;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">完美芦荟沐浴露史：</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">停止使用香皂</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">--</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">在二十世纪八十年代，美国密芝根国立大学（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Michigan State University</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">）的琼斯</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">.</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">卡巴拉教授（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Jon.Kabara</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">）对日常沐浴用的香皂做的一项广泛调查研究，得出一个惊人的结论：香皂的碱性会破坏皮肤表层天然保护油，使皮肤干燥、粗糙；香皂会传染疾病！<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">无独有偶，美国宾夕法尼亚大学（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">University of Pennsylvania</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">）的詹姆斯</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">.</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">莱登教授（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">James Leyden</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">）也作出同样的实验报告，他说细菌可以在干的或湿的香皂上生存长达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">48</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">小时，人们会通过共同使用香皂传染疾病。由于上述原因，新中国人民在八十年代便开始弃香皂而转用沐浴露。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">碱性香皂和沐浴露会伤害皮肤</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">--</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">市面上的香皂和沐浴露绝大部分都是碱性，因为它们具有一定的洁净效能。但许多人却不知道人体的皮肤是属微酸性的，使用碱性的香皂和沐浴露会破坏皮肤表面的天然保护油，使皮肤变得异常绷紧、干燥、且容易衰老。皮肤敏感者会觉得极度不适，皮肤病患者更会使情况恶化。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">完美芦荟沐浴露采用神奇的芦荟精华、昂贵的天然植物润肤乳和太阳花油制成，属微酸性，最接近人体的皮肤，能够</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">100%</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">呵护您的肌肤，不会对皮肤造成碱灼伤，使用最安全！<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27.05pt;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">芦荟对肌肤的益处：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">、清洁肌肤</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">--</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">芦荟所含的酵素能溶解死亡的表皮细胞组织，有利于彻底清除皮肤角质层的死亡细胞。此外，芦荟还可以渗透到毛孔和皮脂腺深处，有利于清除其间的毒素和其它废物，深层彻底地清洁皮肤，能清除导致皮肤的深层隐患；保护皮肤的弱酸性及保留皮脂膜，能使皮肤免受细菌、病菌的侵害；并且芦荟还具有突出的消炎杀菌功效。因而使用芦荟沐浴露能有效预防皮肤病，而不会象普通香皂、沐浴露那样会引发皮肤病（因其会破坏皮肤的弱酸性及皮脂膜，削弱皮肤的免疫机能，并且香皂可成为病菌传染媒介）。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">、激发皮肤活力</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">--</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">深度、彻底地清洁能增强皮肤呼吸。芦荟沐浴露所含成份能增进皮肤的血液循环，促进皮肤细胞吸收养分和排泄废物的功能（新陈代谢），同时也可促进细胞的复健再生，最终从整体上激发皮肤的活力。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">、收敛调和皮肤</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">--</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">芦荟天生的收敛作用能使皮肤坚实而细致，防止皮肤松驰、起皱。芦荟沐浴露的酸碱值是理想的酸碱值，使用芦荟沐浴露后，可以把干性皮肤过高的酸碱性调低（干性皮肤</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">PH</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">值</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">&gt;6.5</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">），也可以把油性皮肤过低的酸碱值调高（油性皮肤</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">PH</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">值&le;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">4.5</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">）。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">4</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">、滋润皮肤</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">--</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">芦荟成份的分子非常小，渗透能力强，可以将水份带入肌肤，并且将丰富的营养素带入皮肤的内层。从而保持皮肤光滑柔嫩，避免皮肤因水份、养份不足而瘙痒。因此，使用芦荟沐浴露对减轻干性皮肤瘙痒有特效。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">5</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">、保护皮肤</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">--</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">芦荟沐浴露中特别添加的润肤乳能锁住皮肤水份，防止皮肤失水干燥，其中所含的营养素和水分还能滋养肌肤；另外，润肤乳还能防止紫外线、细菌、空气污染物等不利因素对皮肤造成的伤害。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27.05pt;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">润肤乳的功效：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-h