上的一些香皂和沐浴露则是碱性的，清洁皮肤以后会令皮肤干燥绷紧，引起发痒。完美芦荟沐浴露含有珍贵的天然植物润肤露，而且是属于微酸性沐浴露，能滋润全身肌肤，防止皮肤干裂。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">、问：为什么使用完美芦荟沐浴露沐浴。皮肤上有一种滑溜溜的感觉？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">答：因为完美芦荟沐浴露含有润肤乳，能有效地将肌肤角质层的水份锁住，令肌肤的滋润程度得以保持。初次使用者也许不习惯，但长期使用会令你爱不释手。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">、问：用沐浴露洗脸为什么出现退皮、绷紧、发热现象？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 27px; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">答：沐浴露的清洁能力较强，干性皮肤不适宜用来洗脸。所以肯定会出现脱皮、绷紧等现象。因为人的脸部肌肤是很敏感、娇嫩的，选择好的洁肤、护肤产品显得非常重要，如果要更好地呵护脸部肌肤，您可以选用完美的玛丽艳洁面产品，它在温和细致地清洁您的脸部肌肤的同时，补充更多的营养、保湿成分，使肌肤清洁亮丽、滋润保湿，倍加呵护。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 27pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:黑体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<div class=\"marginleft\" style=\"margin-left: 14px; font-family: Simsun;\">\r\n<div id=\"txt_ulli\" style=\"width: 706px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span id=\"Label_Content\"> </span></div>\r\n</div>', 'images/201305/thumb_img/213_thumb_G_1369800679289.png', 'images/201305/goods_img/213_G_1369800679447.jpg', 'images/201305/source_img/213_G_1369800679244.png', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1369456004', '70', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1371141958', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '');
