">6ml&times;20</span>包<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:黑体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">产品价格：￥<span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"http://www.perfect99.com/product_pic/BigImages/new_myl_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">产品说明</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#00B050\">:</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">、全新滋养护肤型芦荟沐浴露适用于各型肤质。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">、芦荟沐浴露采用多种高级原料精制而成。蕴含百合科植物芦荟提取物，太阳花油，温和润肤乳等，其</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">pH</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">值接近人体皮肤的酸碱度。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">、温和润肤乳具有清洁肌肤，去除死皮，洗去多余油脂的功效。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">、芦荟提取物，太阳花油能营养、滋润皮肤，并与润肤乳在皮肤表面形成保护膜，使肌肤如丝般幼滑娇嫩。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">、蕴含超浓缩芦荟精华，将面部护理技术运用至全身，细心清洁，呵护您身体的每一寸肌肤。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">、散发自然清香，唤醒您神采飞扬的美丽气质。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">、长期使用，可帮助改善肌肤暗哑，令肌肤莹润有光泽。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">◆：适用于干性</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#00B050\">/</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">中性</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#00B050\">/</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">敏感性</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#00B050\">/</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">极干性肌肤及干燥气候使用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">◆：夏天使用不油腻，冬天使用不干燥。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">产品用法：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">先将皮肤润湿，取适量完美芦荟沐浴露涂于湿润过的皮肤上，用手或沐浴球</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">/</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">海绵轻揉皮肤至泡沫最丰富时，再用清水洗净即可，如重复上述动作（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">DOUBLE ACTION</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">）可达更佳效果。<b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">注意：应存放在通风阴凉处，避免日晒。如不慎入眼，请立即用清水洗净。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><img src=\"http://img.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/84155695/T2czZaXa8XXXXXXXXX_!!84155695.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">完美芦荟沐浴露史：</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">停止使用香皂</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#00B050\">--</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">在二十世纪八十年代，美国密芝根国立大学（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">Michigan State University</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">）的琼斯</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">.</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">卡巴拉教授（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">Jon.Kabara</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">）对日常沐浴用的香皂做的一项广泛调查研究，得出一个惊人的结论：香皂的碱性会破坏皮肤表层天然保护油，使皮肤干燥、粗糙；香皂会传染疾病！<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">无独有偶，美国宾夕法尼亚大学（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#00B050\">University of Pennsylvania</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">）的詹姆斯</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">.</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">莱登教授（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">James Leyden</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">）也作出同样的实验报告，他说细菌可以在干的或湿的香皂上生存长达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">48</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">小时，人们会通过共同使用香皂传染疾病。由于上述原因，新中国人民在八十年代便开始弃香皂而转用沐浴露。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">碱性香皂和沐浴露会伤害皮肤</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#00B050\">--</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">市面上的香皂和沐浴露绝大部分都是碱性，因为它们具有一定的洁净效能。但许多人却不知道人体的皮肤是属微酸性的，使用碱性的香皂和沐浴露会破坏皮肤表面的天然保护油，使皮肤变得异常绷紧、干燥、且容易衰老。皮肤敏感者会觉得极度不适，皮肤病患者更会使情况恶化。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">完美芦荟沐浴露采用神奇的芦荟精华、昂贵的天然植物润肤乳和太阳花油制成，属微酸性，最接近人体的皮肤，能够</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">100%</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">呵护您的肌肤，不会对皮肤造成碱灼伤，使用最安全！<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#00B050\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27.05pt; line-height: 150%;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">芦荟对肌肤的益处：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">、清洁肌肤</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">--</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">芦荟所含的酵素能溶解死亡的表皮细胞组织，有利于彻底清除皮肤角质层的死亡细胞。此外，芦荟还可以渗透到毛孔和皮脂腺深处，有利于清除其间的毒素和其它废物，深层彻底地清洁皮肤，能清除导致皮肤的深层隐患；保护皮肤的弱酸性及保留皮脂膜，能使皮肤免受细菌、病菌的侵害；并且芦荟还具有突出的消炎杀菌功效。因而使用芦荟沐浴露能有效预防皮肤病，而不会象普通香皂、沐浴露那样会引发皮肤病（因其会破坏皮肤的弱酸性及皮脂膜，削弱皮肤的免疫机能，并且香皂可成为病菌传染媒介）。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">、激发皮肤活力</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">--</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">深度、彻底地清洁能增强皮肤呼吸。芦荟沐浴露所含成份能增进皮肤的血液循环，促进皮肤细胞吸收养分和排泄废物的功能（新陈代谢），同时也可促进细胞的复健再生，最终从整体上激发皮肤的活力。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">、收敛调和皮肤</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">--</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">芦荟天生的收敛作用能使皮肤坚实而细致，防止皮肤松驰、起皱。芦荟沐浴露的酸碱值是理想的酸碱值，使用芦荟沐浴露后，可以把干性皮肤过高的酸碱性调低（干性皮肤</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">PH</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">值</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">&gt;6.5</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">），也可以把油性皮肤过低的酸碱值调高（油性皮肤</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">PH</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">值&le;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">4.5</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">）。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">、滋润皮肤</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">--</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">芦荟成份的分子非常小，渗透能力强，可以将水份带入肌肤，并且将丰富的营养素带入皮肤的内层。从而保持皮肤光滑柔嫩，避免皮肤因水份、养份不足而瘙痒。因此，使用芦荟沐浴露对减轻干性皮肤瘙痒有特效。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">、保护皮肤</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">--</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">芦荟沐浴露中特别添加的润肤乳能锁住皮肤水份，防止皮肤失水干燥，其中所含的营养素和水分还能滋养肌肤；另外，润肤乳还能防止紫外线、细菌、空气污染物等不利因素对皮肤造成的伤害。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27.05pt; line-height: 150%;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">润肤乳的功效：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">由于市面上的香皂和沐浴露含碱性强，使皮肤干燥、易衰老，结果部份经济能力较强者在沐浴后使用昂贵的润肤乳滋润全身肌肤以防止水份消失，但不懂这些道理和经济条件不太好的群众呢？现在完美芦荟沐浴露独特的配方添加昂贵的天然植物油润肤乳，能有效的将肌肤角质层</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">NMF</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">Natural Moisturi-sing Factor</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#00B050\">）的水份锁住，防止皮肤干燥，还能在皮肤表面形成一层营养保护膜，补充皮肤营养，起到保湿作用，使肌肤如丝般幼滑娇嫩，让您领略沐浴清爽的感觉。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">使用方法：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">应配合沐浴棉（尼龙网团，商场有售，非沐浴海棉）使用。先用<span lang=\"EN-US\">prefix = st1 ns = &quot;urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags&quot;</span></span><span class=\"apple-converted-space\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">38</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">℃左右的温水将身体彻底淋湿浸透，沐浴棉淋湿后，将</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">滴芦荟沐浴露挤到沐浴棉内层，搓起泡沫后再到全身擦洗，全身擦洗完毕后，用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">38</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">℃温水彻底冲洗即可。若身体较脏，可再重复洗一次，沐浴露半滴就够。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">一定要配合&ldquo;沐浴棉&rdquo;使用，一般用澡巾和沐浴海棉使用许多沐浴露都无法产生满意的泡沫量，导致大量浪费，并有未干净的错觉。而配合&ldquo;沐浴棉&rdquo;使用后，只须一滴就能擦到全身都有较多的泡沫。即使很脏的皮肤用一滴洗两次，也能达到满意的泡沫量，配合使用沐浴棉能把使用沐浴露的消费降到接近使用香皂的消费水平，对打开沐浴露的销路大有帮助。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#00B050\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">注：芦荟沐浴露有排毒功效，少数人在使用后可产生皮肤发痒或出疹现象，应注意合理解释。</span><img src=\"http://img.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/84155695/T2rLcXXilaXXXXXXXX_!!84155695.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/84155695/T2WXkaXktXXXXXXXXX_!!84155695.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/84155695/T2aQsaXalXXXXXXXXX_!!84155695.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/84155695/T2ycgXXixaXXXXXXXX_!!84155695.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:26.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">产</span></b><span class=\"apple-converted-space\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:26.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">&nbsp;</span></b></span><b><span style=\"font-size:26.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">品</span></b><span class=\"apple-converted-space\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:26.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">&nbsp;</span></b></span><b><span style=\"font-size:26.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">问</span></b><span class=\"apple-converted-space\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:26.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">&nbsp;</span></b></span><b><span style=\"font-size:26.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">、问：我经常在洗澡后皮肤发痒，请问是什么原因？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：人的皮肤是微酸性的，而市面上的一些香皂和沐浴露则是碱性的，清洁皮肤以后会令皮肤干燥绷紧，引起发痒。完美芦荟沐浴露含有珍贵的天然植物润肤露，而且是属于微酸性沐浴露，能滋润全身肌肤，防止皮肤干裂。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">、问：为什么使用完美芦荟沐浴露沐浴。皮肤上有一种滑溜溜的感觉？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：因为完美芦荟沐浴露含有润肤乳，能有效地将肌肤角质层的水份锁住，令肌肤的滋润程度得以保持。初次使用者也许不习惯，但长期使用会令你爱不释手。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">、问：用沐浴露洗脸为什么出现退皮、绷紧、发热现象？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：沐浴露的清洁能力较强，干性皮肤不适宜用来洗脸。所以肯定会出现脱皮、绷紧等现象。因为人的脸部肌肤是很敏感、娇嫩的，选择好的洁肤、护肤产品显得非常重要，如果要更好地呵护脸部肌肤，您可以选用完美的玛丽艳洁面产品，它在温和细致地清洁您的脸部肌肤的同时，补充更多的营养、保湿成分，使肌肤清洁亮丽、滋润保湿，倍加呵护。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:黑体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<div class=\"marginleft\" style=\"margin-left: 14px; font-family: Simsun;\">\r\n<div id=\"txt_ulli\" style=\"width: 706px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span id=\"Label_Content\"> </span></div>\r\n</div>', 'images/201305/thumb_img/214_thumb_G_1369800089317.png', 'images/201305/goods_img/214_G_1369800089749.jpg', 'images/201305/source_img/214_G_1369800089757.png', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1369456004', '69', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1371141730', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '');
